%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canada%20Plane%20Diverted%20After%2016-Year-Old%20Attacks%20Family%20Mid-Air%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20unexpected%20disruption%20occurred%20on%20an%20Air%20Canada%20flight%20when%20a%2016-year-old%20passenger%20attacked%20a%20family%20member%20during%20the%20flight.%20The%20unusual%20situation%20resulted%20in%20a%20drastic%20detour%20and%20a%20three-hour%20wait%20for%20the%20passengers%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Ftravel%2Fairline-news%2F2024%2F01%2F05%2Fair-canada-flight-diverted%2F72121237007%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20Canada%20Flight%20137%20was%20en%20route%20from%20Toronto%20to%20Calgary%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rcmp-grc.gc.ca%2Fen%2Fnews%2F2024%2Fwinnipeg-international-airport-rcmp-respond-flight-diversion%5C%22%3Epress%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police.%20The%20Winnipeg%20Richardson%20International%20Airport%20was%20notified%20of%20an%20aircraft%20diversion%20to%20Winnipeg%20at%2012%3A20%20p.m.%20local%20time%2C%20according%20to%20police%2C%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Ban%20unruly%20passenger%20on%20board%20who%20had%20assaulted%20a%20passenger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20has%20determined%20that%20Air%20Canada%20flight%20%23137%20was%20en%20route%20from%20Toronto%20to%20Calgary%2C%20when%20a%2016-year-old%20male%20passenger%2C%20from%20Grande%20Prairie%2C%20assaulted%20an%20adult%20male%20passenger%20who%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20family%20member.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%20the%2016-year-old%20was%20restrained%20by%20fellow%20travellers%20and%20airline%20staff.%20They%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20family%20member%20received%20treatment%20for%20%26quot%3Bminor%20physical%20injuries%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20flight%20and%20the%20teenager%20was%20detained%20and%20transferred%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20medical%20examination.%20No%20other%20injuries%20were%20reported%20and%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20attack%20remains%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20a%20three-hour%20delay%20before%20the%20plane%20could%20continue%20its%20journey%20to%20Calgary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Air%20Canada%20has%20been%20in%20the%20news%20for%20some%20time.%20In%20October%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-mp-claims-he-was-stopped-from-boarding-flight-over-his-name-4514834%5C%22%3EBritish%20MP%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20stopped%20from%20getting%20on%20an%20Air%20Canada%20flight%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebecause%20of%20his%20name.%20Bedford%20Labour%20MP%20Mohammad%20Yasin%20was%20scheduled%20to%20travel%20to%20Canada%20along%20with%20several%20other%20MPs%20from%20the%20Commons%20Housing%2C%20Communities%2C%20and%20Levelling%20Up%20Committee%2C%20but%20he%20was%20detained%20for%20further%20interrogation.%20He%20was%20told%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20his%20name%20was%20Mohammad''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20BBC%2C%20Mr%20Yasin%20was%20stopped%20both%20at%20immigration%20at%20Heathrow%20and%20on%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20UK%20in%20Toronto.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20questioned%20at%20Heathrow%20Airport%20check-in%20by%20Air%20Canada%20officials%20and%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20carrying%20a%20knife%20or%20other%20offensive%20weapon.%20The%20MP%20faced%20similar%20questions%20from%20officials%20on%20his%20return%20trip%20to%20the%20UK.%20He%20was%20eventually%20allowed%20to%20board%20after%20proving%20his%20identity%20as%20an%20MP%20and%20presenting%20a%20valid%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bstressful%20and%20humiliating%26quot%3B.%20The%20MP%20told%20BBC%2C%20''It%20was%20stressful%20and%20humiliating%20to%20be%20singled%20out%20in%20such%20an%20aggressive%20way%20by%20immigration%20control%2C%20especially%20when%20travelling%20in%20a%20group%20as%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20British%20Parliament%20on%20long-arranged%20committee%20business.%20While%20I%20don't%20expect%20special%20treatment%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20it%20does%20concern%20me%20that%20had%20I%20not%20been%20an%20MP%2C%20how%20much%20worse%20the%20experience%20might%20have%20been.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704595740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2Fv89umlv8_air-canada_625x300_13_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-plane-diverted-after-16-year-old-attacks-family-mid-air-4814931%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20family%20member%20received%20treatment%20for%20%26quot%3Bminor%20physical%20injuries%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20flight%20and%20the%20teenager%20was%20detained%20and%20transferred%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20medical%20examination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-plane-diverted-after-16-year-old-attacks-family-mid-air-4814931%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-plane-diverted-after-16-year-old-attacks-family-mid-air-4814931%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-plane-diverted-after-16-year-old-attacks-family-mid-air-4814931%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justin%20Trudeau's%20Plane%20Breaks%20Down%20Again%2C%20Second%20Time%20Since%20G20%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20faced%20a%20minor%20setback%20during%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20as%20an%20aircraft%20glitch%20prompted%20the%20Canadian%20Armed%20Forces%20to%20send%20a%20second%20plane%20with%20a%20repair%20team%20to%20address%20the%20snag.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C