22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENicholas%20Godejohn%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20victim%20of%20hers%20to%20some%20extent.%20I%20do%20think%20his%20sentence%20of%20life%20in%20prison%20without%20the%20possibility%20of%20parole%20is%20wildly%20excessive.%20At%20least%20he%20should%20have%20had%20the%20opportunity%20for%20parole%2C%20considering%20that%20he's%20autistic%2C%20and%20that%20wasn't%20brought%20up%20at%20his%20criminal%20hearing%20because%20there%20was%20some%20dispute%20about%20just%20how%20autistic%20he%20was.%20But%20Gypsy%20Rose%20had%20the%20presence%20to%20buy%20the%20knife%2C%20give%20it%20to%20him%2C%20and%20tell%20him%20what%20she%20wanted%20him%20to%20do.%20He%20is%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20extremely%20suggestible%2C%20so%20we%20can't%20paint%20her%20as%20all%20victim%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20paint%20her%20as%20all%20perpetrator.%20She's%20complex%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20this%20story%20may%20last%20in%20the%20media%20for%20some%20time%2C%20and%20books%20will%20come%20out%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%20the%20one%20that%20Gypsy%20herself%20has%20authored%20with%20the%20help%20of%20two%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20interesting%20that%20you%20bring%20up%20manipulation%20because%20I%20was%20going%20to%20ask%20about%20that%20in%20the%20context%20of%20her%20social%20media%20presence.%20I%20had%20seen%20a%20previous%20interview%20of%20yours%20where%20you%20talked%20about%20how%20many%20media%20appearances%20she's%20done.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20you%20speculated%20that%20at%20least%20some%20part%20of%20her%20giving%20interviews%20has%20to%20be%20a%20form%20of%20manipulation.%20Do%20you%20still%20believe%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20is%20part%20of%20her%20manipulation%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20very%20inviting%20if%20you%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20make%20money%20or%20get%20attention.%20She%20was%20raised%20by%20a%20mother%20who%20was%20a%20world%20expert%20at%20manipulating%20attention%20and%20control%20and%20was%20isolated%20from%20others%20who%20would%20have%20perhaps%20illustrated%20healthier%20behaviors.%20So%2C%20I'm%20not%20surprised%20that%20things%20have%20unfolded%20the%20way%20they%20have.%20I%20do%20worry.%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20necessarily%20bad%20%E2%80%94%20psychologically%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20it%20doesn't%20last%20too%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20she%20trying%20to%20manipulate%20people%20into%20thinking%20or%20doing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20propelled%20by%20other%20people%20%E2%80%94%20though%20stemming%20from%20her%20own%20self-interest%20%E2%80%94%20Gypsy%20is%20looking%20to%20become%20financially%20secure%20and%20to%20have%20her%20reputation%20redeemed.%20She%20has%20always%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20intense%20interest%2C%20and%20she%20and%20her%20hangers-on%20know%20it%20%E2%80%94%20my%20comments%20in%20this%20regard%20exclude%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frod-kristy-blanchard-gypsy-rose-blanchard-family-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20seem%20sincerely%20interested%20in%20her%20well-being.%20She%20has%20little%20education%20and%20no%20evident%20job%20skills%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20blame%20her%20for%20seeking%20money%20for%20her%20story%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20that%20she%20isn't%20surprised%20or%20upset%20when%20interest%20fades%2C%20as%20it%20eventually%20will.%20I%20was%20a%20little%20taken%20aback%20by%20one%20of%20her%20TikTok%20posts%2C%20in%20which%20she%20carefully%20gives%20the%20titles%20of%20her%20e-book%20and%20Lifetime%20docuseries.%20If%20she%20doesn't%20have%20a%20personal%20publicist%2C%20it%20sure%20sounds%20like%20she%20does.%20That%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing%20for%20now%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20she%20realizes%20they%20may%20not%20necessarily%20have%20her%20best%20interests%20at%20heart%20in%20the%20short-%20or%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanchard%20is%20likely%20dealing%20with%20some%20sort%20of%20trauma%20from%20her%20childhood.%20Is%20the%20internet%2C%20where%20Gypsy's%20every%20move%20is%20now%20being%20watched%2C%20a%20good%20place%20for%20her%20to%20be%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20there%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20her%20to%20accept%20every%20media%20opportunity%20and%20stay%20very%20involved%20with%20social%20media%20because%20not%20only%20does%20she%20need%20to%20make%20money%2C%20but%20there%20are%20people%20around%20her%20who%20want%20to%20make%20money%20off%20her.%20I%20saw%20that%20post%20that%20says%20how%20strange%20it%20was%20that%20her%20husband%20looked%20like%20her%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emother.%20They're%20both%20overweight%20%E2%80%94%20otherwise%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20it.%20And%20there%20was%20a%20whole%20spate%20of%20comments%20endorsing%20that.%20People%20have%20the%20anonymity%20of%20the%20internet%20and%20can%20be%20variable%20in%20how%20they%20feel%20about%20situations.%20So%20if%20somebody%20posts%20something%20unbecoming%20or%20hostile%2C%20there's%20always%20somebody%20who%20will%20jump%20on%20board%2C%20whether%20intentionally%20or%20not%2C%20and%20start%20a%20whole%20battery%20of%20posts%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20make%20sense%20for%20someone%20else%20neutral%20to%20screen%20these%20posts.%20From%20what%20I%20can%20tell%2C%20her%20family%20seems%20loving%2C%20supportive%2C%20and%20protective.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20hope%20she'd%20focus%20on%20people%20with%20no%20agenda%20other%20than%20to%20help%20her%20heal%20and%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20best%20for%20Gypsy%2C%20psychologically%2C%20as%20someone%20recovering%20from%20this%20type%20of%20abuse%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENobody%20really%20seems%20to%20be%20asking%20the%20question%20of%20what%20is%20best%20psychologically%20for%20Gypsy%2C%20and%20I%20wish%20more%20people%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20if%20you're%20familiar%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fverdict-in-take-care-of-maya-maya-kowalski-case-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaya%20Kowalski%3C%2Fa%3E%20case%20in%20Florida%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebut%20my%20first%20reaction%20when%20Gypsy's%20name%20started%20showing%20up%20online%2C%20to%20be%20honest%20with%20you%2C%20was%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20thing%20that%20stories%20about%20Gypsy%20have%20now%20totally%20preempted%20the%20falsehoods%20about%20the%20Kowalski%20case%20and%20medical%20child%20abuse.%20Because%20for%20a%20while%2C%20all%20anyone%20wanted%20to%20talk%20about%20was%20how%20false%20accusations%20of%20medical%20child%20abuse%20crop%20up%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20not%20true.%20Now%2C%20with%20Gypsy%20Rose's%20visibility%2C%20who%20can%20honestly%20say%20this%20is%20a%20false%20diagnosis%3F%20So%20I%2C%20for%20selfish%20reasons%2C%20perhaps%20as%20well%20as%20professional%20reasons%2C%20like%20that%20she's%20as%20public%20as%20she%20has%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20needs%20to%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20hard%20for%20her%20to%20find%20therapy%20with%20somebody%20who's%20really%20knowledgeable.%20There%20tends%20still%20to%20be%20very%20little%20training%20about%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy.%20I%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20it%2C%20even%20though%20I%20went%20through%20a%20psychiatric%20residency%2C%20until%20after%20I%20was%20on%20the%20faculty%20of%20Duke.%20But%20I%20hope%20she%20can%20find%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20support%20groups%20for%20survivors%20through%20a%20website%20called%20munchausensupport.com.%20I%20would%20love%20that%20resource%20to%20be%20available%20to%20Gypsy%20as%20long%20as%20her%20story%2C%20which%20is%20so%20extreme%2C%20doesn't%20dominate%20and%20the%20other%20survivors%20don't%20get%20heard.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20big%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Gypsy%20Rose's%20story%20drown%20out%20other%20other%20abuse%20victims%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20she's%20called%20attention%20to%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%20like%20no%20one%20else%2C%20most%20cases%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20every%20other%20case%20of%20which%20I'm%20aware%20%E2%80%94%20don't%20involve%20the%20murder%20of%20the%20mom.%20Her%20case%20lasted%20her%20whole%20childhood%20and%20adolescence.%20That's%20unusual.%20Most%20cases%20simply%20involve%20a%20perpetrator%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20always%20the%20child's%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20who%20makes%20false%20reports%20about%20the%20child's%20symptoms%20or%20exaggerates%20them%20to%20a%20doctor.%20And%20maybe%20that'll%20be%20figured%20out%20quickly%2C%20maybe%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20not%20lose%20focus%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20almost%20all%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmother-accused-injuring-son-munchausen-by-proxy-2017-12%3F_gl%3D1*4olkls*_ga*NTExMzU3MzY2LjE2OTM2MTI2OTk.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcwNDUyNjM0MS4xMDAxLjEuMTcwNDUyNjQ2Ni41MC4wLjA.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMunchausen%20by%20proxy%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20mild%20and%20subtle.%20But%20doctors%20need%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20recognize%20them%20and%20not%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20this%20is%20nothing%20like%20Gypsy%20Rose's%20case%2C%20so%20it%20can't%20be%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%2C%20and%20I%20better%20not%20make%20a%20report%20to%20the%20police%20or%20Child%20Protective%20Services.%26quot%3B%20That%20would%20be%20a%20disservice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20testified%20in%20a%20case%20where%20the%20guardian%20ad%20litem%20got%20her%20information%20about%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%20from%20watching%20%26quot%3BThe%20Act.%26quot%3B%20I%20testified%20that%20would%20be%20grossly%20misleading%20to%20her%20unless%20she%20found%20other%20more%20nuanced%20sources%20of%20information.%20I%20was%20worried%20that%20she%20would%20be%20dismissive%20of%20the%20case%20at%20hand%20because%20it%20wasn't%20as%20extreme.%3C