im%20long%20enough%20for%20some%20students%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20cafeteria.%20That's%20just%20Dad%2C%26quot%3B%20Claire%20Marburger's%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriday's%20statement%20from%20the%20state%20DPS%20appeared%20to%20corroborate%20Claire%20Marburger's%20comments%2C%20though%20details%20remained%20limited%20amid%20the%20active%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20thus%20far%20confirms%20Principal%20Marburger%20acted%20selflessly%20and%20placed%20himself%20in%20harm's%20way%20in%20an%20apparent%20effort%20to%20protect%20his%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department's%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaire%20Marburger%20added%20that%20her%20father%20would%20joke%20that%20%26quot%3Bhis%20ugly%20face%20is%20popping%20up%20too%20much%20online%2C%20as%20he%20is%20getting%20attention%20as%20he%20is%20a%20deserving%20hero.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20other%20victim's%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20post.%20%26quot%3BShow%20grace%20to%20the%20Butler%20family%2C%20as%20we%20are%20not%20our%20kid's%20mistakes%20and%20actions%20or%20our%20parent's%20mistakes%20and%20actions.%20Remember%20this%20is%20something%20Dylan's%20family%20has%20to%20live%20with%20too%2C%20as%20well%20as%20losing%20their%20child.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiowa-school-principal-talked-shooter-kids-escape-daughter-says-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704579144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6599bdf16979d7371821131b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiowa-school-principal-talked-shooter-kids-escape-daughter-says-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20school%20shooting%20in%20Iowa%20left%20two%20dead%20and%20seven%20injured.%20Among%20those%20hurt%20was%20the%20principal%2C%20who%20acted