d%20puffiness%20%E2%80%94%20essentially%20giving%20the%20eyes%20a%20more%20youthful%20look.%20After%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-rhinoplasty-deviated-septum-surgery-recovery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enose%20jobs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eye%20lifts%20have%20become%20the%20one%20of%20the%20most%20requested%20plastic%20surgery%20procedures%20in%20the%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.com%2Farticle%2Feyes-profile-november-issue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Vogue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Society%20of%20Plastic%20Surgeons%20says%20the%20blepharoplasty%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plasticsurgery.org%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Famerican-society-of-plastic-surgeons-reveals-2022s-most-sought-after-procedures%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efifth-most%20common%20procedure%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country%20in%202022%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20year%20for%20which%20data%20is%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20is%20to%20remove%20all%20of%20the%20extra%20skin%20that%20might%20have%20accumulated%20on%20the%20eye%20as%20a%20result%20of%20aging%2C%20gravity%2C%20and%20loss%20of%20elasticity%2C%26quot%3B%20Carolyn%20Chang%2C%20San%20Francisco%20based%20plastic%20surgeon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allure.com%2Fstory%2Fblepharoplasty-eyelid-lift%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20Allure%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Though%20it's%20largely%20a%20cosmetic%20procedure%2C%20it%20can%20improve%20eyesight%2C%20especially%20for%20people%20whose%20field%20of%20vision%20has%20been%20obstructed%20by%20sagging%20eyelids%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmy.clevelandclinic.org%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2F8409-eyelid-surgery-blepharoplasty%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20Cleveland%20Clinic%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Beye-lift%26quot%3B%20and%20how%20much%20does%20it%20cost%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20versions%20of%20the%20procedure%3A%20One%20for%20the%20upper%20eyelids%20and%20one%20for%20the%20lower%20eyelids.%20And%20though%20the%20aims%20are%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20to%20cut%20back%20excess%20skin%20and%20trim%20fatty%20tissue%20around%20the%20eyes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20the%20surgical%20techniques%20are%20different.%20Depending%20on%20whether%20a%20patient%20opts%20to%20treat%20their%20upper%20or%20lower%20eyelids%20(or%20both)%20the%20procedure%20can%20take%20anywhere%20from%2045%20minutes%20to%20two%20hours%2C%20according%20to%20Cleveland%20Clinic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20generally%20a%20painless%20surgery%20where%20complications%20are%20rare%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20is%20a%20good%20candidate.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20the%20doctor%20suggests%20a%20blepharoplasty%20when%20the%20patient%20really%20needs%20a%20brow%20lift%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20David%20Rosenberg%2C%20a%20facial%20plastic%20and%20reconstructive%20surgeon%20in%20New%20York%20City%20told%20Allure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20blepharoplasty%20is%20%243%2C339%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plasticsurgery.org%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fblepharoplasty-patients-are-getting-younger-heres-why%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20American%20Society%20of%20Plastic%20Surgeons%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20pricing%20can%20vary%20upon%20location%2C%20complexity%20of%20the%20procedure%2C%20and%20whether%20a%20patient%20is%20opting%20for%20an%20upper%20or%20lower%20blepharoplasty.%20In%20New%20York%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20patient%20could%20expect%20to%20shell%20out%20%248%2C000%20for%20an%20upper%20eyelid%20procedure%2C%20and%20%249%2C000%20for%20a%20lower%20one%2C%20New%20York%20based%20plastic%20surgeon%20Dr.%20Lara%20Devgan%2C%20told%20Allure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemote%20work%20is%20driving%20a%20eye-lift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eboom%20among%2030%20year-olds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20blepharoplasty%20candidates%20are%20typically%20patients%20in%20their%20fifties%20and%20older%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20younger%20generations%20have%20increasingly%20been%20expressing%20interest%20in%20the%20procedure.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20actress%20Amanda%20Bynes%20revealed%20that%20she%20underwent%20the%20surgery%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40amandaamandaamanda1986%2Fvideo%2F7311461218122812715%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20on%20TikTok%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20I%20could%20have%20ever%20done%20for%20my%20self-confidence%2C%20and%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20a%20lot%20better%20in%20my%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Schwarcz%2C%20an%20oculoplastic%20surgeon%20based%20in%20New%20York%2C%20has%20also%20seen%20a%20notable%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20patients%20in%20their%20thirties%20coming%20to%20him%20for%20consultations%2C%20according%20to%20Vogue.%20He%20suspects%20that%20it%20has%20something%20to%20with%20all%20the%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzoom-video-conferencing-filter-touch-up-work-from-home-coronavirus-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eremote%20workers%20have%20been%20spending%20staring%20at%20their%20faces%20on%20Zoom%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20now%20comparing%20your%20face%20to%20your%20colleagues'%2C%20even%20though%20you're%20supposed%20to%20be%20doing%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20convenience%20of%20working%20from%20home%20has%20also%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20quietly%20recover%20from%20a%20blepharoplasty%20%E2%80%94%20and%20evade%20questions%20from%20curious%20colleagues.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20working%20from%20home%20virtually%2C%20there%20is%20overall%20a%20much%20larger%20volume%20of%20facial%20surgery%20because%20it%20is%20now%20easier%20to%20hide%20during%20the%20healing%20process%20and%20a%20heightened%20awareness%20of%20one's%20facial%20appearance%2C%26quot%3B%20San%20Francisco-based%20Dr.%20Chang%20told%20the%20American%20Society%20of%20Plastic%20Surgeons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Dr.%20Chang%20had%20noticed%20interest%20picking%20up%20among%20younger%20generations%20even%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20especially%20as%20social%20media%20influencers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-kim-kardashian-west-career-evolution-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20Kardashians%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20helped%20reduce%20the%20stigma%20around%20plastic%20surgery.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20social%20media%20%E2%80%93%20in%20particular%2C%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20popular%20press%20are%20also%20contributing%20to%20the%20desire%20for%20younger%20patients%20to%20seek%20out%20eyelid%20surgeries%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20American%20Society%20of%20Plastic%20Surgeons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-eye-lift-is-surging-in-popularity-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704576811000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6599c7076979d7371821133d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-eye-lift-is-surging-in-popularity-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Plastic%20surgeons%20say%20people%20have%20been%20spending%20too%20much%20time%20looking%20at%20themselves%20on%20Zoom%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20fueling%20interest%20in%20eye%20lifts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fth