rruption%20charges.%20The%20party%20has%20called%20a%2048-hour%20nationwide%20general%20strike%2C%20which%20began%20at%206%20am%20on%20Saturday.%20Party%20spokesperson%20Ruhul%20Kabir%20Rizvi%20said%20the%20strike%20was%20aimed%20at%20pressing%20for%20their%20demands%20for%20%26quot%3Bresignation%20of%20the%20illegal%20government%2C%20establishment%20of%20a%20non-party%20neutral%20government%20and%20release%20of%20all%20party%20leaders%20and%20activists%20from%20prison%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20have%20been%20incidents%20of%20violence%20and%20arson%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%20At%20least%20five%20schools%2C%20including%20four%20designated%20as%20polling%20centres%20for%20the%20general%20election%2C%20have%20been%20set%20ablaze.%20Four%20coaches%20of%20the%20Jessore-Dhaka%20Benapole%20Express%20were%20also%20set%20on%20fire%20on%20Friday%2C%20killing%20four%20people.%20Arson%20related%20to%20the%20polls%20is%20suspected%20in%20both%20incidents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKazi%20Habibul%20Awal%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20said%20there%20is%20no%20question%20about%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20elections.%C2%A0%26quot%3BOne%20issue%20is%20violence%20is%20visible%20and%20the%20voters%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20violence.%20If%20it%20is%20repeated%2C%20that%20may%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20voters%20in%20turning%20up%20at%20polling%20stations%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20admitting%20that.%20But%20we%20have%20engaged%208%20lakh%20law%20enforcement%20personnel%2C%20all%20well-armed%2C%20who%20will%20be%20on%20duty%20during%20polling%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHad%20BNP%20participated%20in%20the%20election%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20more%20competitive%2C%20more%20inclusive%20and%20more%20festive.%20That%20is%20a%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESheikh%20Hasina%2C%20whose%20government%20has%20arrested%20thousands%20of%20rival%20politicians%20and%20supporters%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%2C%20has%20urged%20pro-democratic%20and%20law-abiding%20parties%20not%20to%20fuel%20ideas%20that%20%26quot%3Bdisrupt%26quot%3B%20the%20country's%20constitutional%20process%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20is%20credited%20with%20turning%20around%20the%20country's%20economy%20and%20supercharging%20its%20garments%20industry.%20The%20growth%20has%2C%20however%2C%20slowed%20since%20mid-2022%20and%20experts%20have%20said%20economic%20stability%20will%20be%20a%20major%20challenge%20for%20the%20next%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20100%20foreign%20observers%2C%20including%20three%20from%20India%2C%20will%20monitor%20the%20election.%20India%20has%20said%20the%20election%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Binternal%20matter%26quot%3B%20while%20some%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20have%20called%20for%20credible%20and%20inclusive%20polls%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVoting%20will%20be%20held%20for%20300%20constituencies%20in%20the%20350-strong%20Parliament%20-%20the%20Jatiyo%20Shangsad.%20The%20other%2050%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20women%20and%20are%20allotted%20based%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20Parliament%20after%20the%20election.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENearly%202%2C000%20candidates%20are%20in%20the%20fray%20and%20a%20record%205.1%25%20of%20them%20are%20women.%20Voting%20will%20begin%20at%208%20am%20local%20time%20-%20when%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20is%20expected%20to%20cast%20her%20ballot%20-%C2%A0and%20end%20at%204%20pm.%20Counting%20will%20start%20after%20voting%20ends%20and%20initial%20results%20are%20expected%20by%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704565860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Frc6euk7g_bangladesh-election_625x300_06_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-elections-bangladesh-polls-sheikh-hasina-pm-hasina-likely-to-win