20'So%20You%20Think%20You%20Can%20Dance'%20of%20my%20decision%20to%20step%20back%20from%20participating%20in%20this%20year's%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20Lythgoe%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20so%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20but%20entirely%20voluntarily%20because%C2%A0this%20great%20program%20has%20always%20been%20about%20dance%20and%20dancers%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20its%20focus%20needs%20to%20remain.%C2%A0In%20the%20meantime%2C%20I%20am%20dedicating%20myself%20to%20clearing%20my%20name%20and%20restoring%20my%20reputation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20previously%20provided%20to%20BI%2C%20Lythgoe%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%20and%20saddened%26quot%3B%20by%20Abdul's%20allegations%20and%20that%20her%20claims%20were%20untrue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20more%20than%20two%20decades%2C%20Paula%20and%20I%20have%20interacted%20as%20dear%20%E2%80%94and%20entirely%20platonic%20%E2%80%94%20friends%20and%20colleagues%2C%26quot%3B%20Lythgoe%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%20%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20however%2C%20out%20of%20the%20blue%2C%20I%20learned%20of%20these%20claims%20in%20the%20press%20and%20I%20want%20to%20be%20clear%3A%20not%20only%20are%20they%20false%2C%20they%20are%20deeply%20offensive%20to%20me%20and%20to%20everything%20I%20stand%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDouglas%20Johnson%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Abdul%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20singer%20should%20be%20commended%20for%20her%20courage%20to%20come%20forward%20with%20the%20accusations%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20when%20the%20alleged%20abuser%20is%20a%20figure%20so%20dominant%20in%20her%20profession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20clearly%20a%20difficult%20decision%20to%20make%2C%20but%20Ms.%20Abdul%20knows%20that%20she%20stands%20both%20in%20the%20shoes%20and%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20many%20other%20similarly%20situated%20survivors%2C%20and%20she%20is%20determined%20to%20see%20that%20justice%20is%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbdul's%20lawsuit%20also%20accuses%20Lythgoe%20of%20groping%20one%20of%20her%20assistants%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20survivor%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20you%20can%20call%20the%20National%20Sexual%20Assault%20Hotline%20(1-800-656-4673)%20or%20visit%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhotline.rainn.org%2Fonline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eits%20website%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20receive%20confidential%20support.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fso-you-think-you-can-dance-judge-resigns-assault-claims-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704565556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65998a6d1c5c7b8c9a0e9c80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fso-you-think-you-can-dance-judge-resigns-assault-claims-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Long%20time%20%26quot%3BSo%20You%20Think%20You%20Can%20Dance%26quot%3B%20judge%20Nigel%20Lythgoe%20resigned%20from%20the%20show%20after%20Paula%20Abdul%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault%20in%20a%20lawsuit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fso-you-think-you-can-dance-judge-resigns-assault-claims-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Less%20Than%20Respectable%20Share%20Of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Seats%20In%20Bihar%20Will...%3A%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20Saturday%20claimed%20that%20a%20less%20than%20%26quot%3Brespectable%26quot%3B%20share%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Bihar%20would%20affect%20not%20just%20the%20party%2C%20but%20the%20entire%20ruling%20%E2%80%98Mahagathbandhan'%2C%20including%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JD(U).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20president%20Akhilesh%20Prasad%20Singh%20made%20the%20statement%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20speculations%20in%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20that%20the%20party%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20settle%20for%20not%20more%20than%20four%20out%20of%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Mahagathbandhan%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20including%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20will%20suffer%20if%20the%20Congress%20fights%20only%20four%20seats%2C%20though%20it%20is%20not%20our%20case%20that%20we%20be%20given%20nine%20just%20because%20we%20had%20contested%20that%20many%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20have%20surfaced%20in%20a%20section%20of%20media%20that%20JD(U)%20wants%2017%20seats%20for%20itself%2C%20as%20many%20as%20it%20had%20contested%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20winning%20all%20but%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20aide%20of%20Kumar%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20for%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20a%20number%20less%20than%2016%2C%20its%20current%20strength%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20was%20out%20of%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%2016%20seats.%20On%20these%2C%20the%20question%20of%20a%20claim%20or%20any%20confusion%20should%20not%20arise%2C%E2%80%9D%20JD(U)%20national%20general%20secretary%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Jha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJha%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Bwhatever%20may%20be%20the%20demand%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20should%20convey%20the%20same%20to%20the%20RJD.%20We%20will%20be%20sitting%20across%20the%20table%20with%20the%20RJD%20for%20final%20discussions%20on%20seat%20sharing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(U)%20leader's%20averment%20was%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20general%20understanding%20reached%20within%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20that%20since%20the%20chief%20minister's%20party%20was%20a%20new%20entrant%2C%20having%20joined%20the%20coalition%20after%20dumping%20the%20BJP%20less%20than%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20RJD%2C%20the%20largest%20constituent%2C%20be%20allowed%20to%20negotiate%20on%20behalf%20of%20smaller%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20to%20this%20effect%20was%20made%20some%20time%20ago%20by%20CPI%20(ML)%20Liberation%20general%20secretary%20Dipankar%20Bhattacharya%2C%20who%20had%20said%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20his%20party%20desired%20has%20been%20shared%20with%20RJD%20supremo%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20who%20would%20negotiate%20on%20behalf%20of%20other%20junior%20partners%20with%20the%20JD(U).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20RJD%20leader%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20hinted%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20the%20party%20wanted%20to%20contest%20and%20Prasad's%20son%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20the%20deputy%20CM%2C%20denied%20having%20taken%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20the%20CM%20and%20I%20am%20the%20deputy.%20There%20can%20be%20any%20number%20of%20issues%20for%20us%20to%20discuss.%20Do%20not%20worry%20too%20much%20about%20seat-sharing.%20We%20will%20let%20you%20know%20in%20due%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav%2C%20when%20journalists%20approached%20him%20with%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahagathbandhan%20leaders%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20RJD%2C%20which%20is%20numerically%20far%20superior%20to%20the%20JD(U)%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20have%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20bargaining%20power%20has%2C%20however%2C%20been%20hit%20because%20of%20its%20dismal%20performance%20in%20the%20general%20elections%20of%202019%20when%20it%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20which%20then%20included%20JD(U)%2C%20had%20won%2039%20out%20of%2040%20seats%20while%20the%20Congress%20bagged%20Kishanganj%2C%20becoming%20the%20lone%20Mahagathbandhan%20constituent%20to%20have%20escaped%20the%20ignominy%20of%20drawing%20a%20blank%20at%20the%20hustings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20added%20it%20was%20unlikely%20that%20the%20RJD%20would%20agree%20to%20a%20share%20smaller%20than%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Kumar%20has%20indicated%20that%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20polls%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20who%20will%20lead%20the%20charge%20for%20the%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20event%20of%20both%20JD(U)%20and%20RJD%20deciding%20to%20contest%2017%20seats%20each%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20CPI(ML)%20L%2C%20CPI%20and%20CPI(M)%20will%20have%20to%20be%20accommodated%20in%20the%20remaining%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Kumar%20Jha%20was%20also%20asked%20whether%20by%20insisting%20on%20a%20high%20number%20of%20seats%2C%20JD(U)%20was%20trying%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20Congress%20for%20naming%20Kumar%20as%20the%20convenor%20of%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNitish%20Kumar%20has%20already%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20has%20forged%20opposition%20unity%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20He%20desires%20nothing%20for%20himself.%20We%20want%20seat-sharing%20to%20be%20complete%20by%20this%20month%20because%20this%20was%20the%20view%20expressed%20by%20our%20leader%20at%20last%20month's%20INDIA%20meet%20in%20Delhi.%20He%20feels%20we%20cannot%20afford%20to%20lose%20much%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Akhilesh%20Prasad%20Singh%20was%20asked%20the%20same%20question%2C%20he%20replied%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20has%20great%20appreciation%20for%20the%20contribution%20made%20by%20Kumar%20in%20cobbling%20together%20the%20coalition.%20But%2C%20to%20name%20him%20as%20the%20convenor%20is%20not%20entirely%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20our%20party.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20consensus%20among%20other%20constituents%20of%20INDIA.%20Talks%20are%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndi