ated-in-just-18-minutes-13043118%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMacaulay%20Was%20Sent%20By%20British%20To%20Enslave%20Indians%20Mentally%26quot%3B%3A%20Rajnath%20Singh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20on%20Saturday%20said%20Thomas%20Babington%20Macaulay%20was%20sent%20to%20India%20to%20throttle%20the%20country's%20traditional%20system%20of%20education%20and%20enslave%20Indians%20mentally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20revival%20of%20%3Cem%3E'gurukuls'%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20necessary%20to%20counter%20the%20effects%20of%20Macaulay's%20system%20of%20education%20on%20Indian%20minds%20but%20advised%20that%20these%20traditional%20schools%20should%20synthesise%20their%20education%20with%20emerging%20technologies%20like%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20quantum%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMacaulay%20was%20sent%20to%20India%20to%20enslave%20Indians%20even%20mentally%20by%20colonising%20their%20minds%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20addressing%20a%20large%20gathering%20of%20seers%20and%20students%20at%20the%20foundation%20laying%20ceremony%20of%20Patanjali%20Gurukulam%20in%20Haridwar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Macaulay's%20attitude%20of%20disregard%20towards%20India's%20cultural%20and%20literary%20legacy%2C%20the%20Union%20minister%20said%20the%20British%20official%20had%20once%20declared%20that%20an%20almirah%20in%20a%20European%20library%20was%20worth%20the%20whole%20of%20India's%20literary%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Macaulay)%20said%20this%20about%20a%20country%20that%20created%20the%20Vedas%2C%20the%20Upanishads%20and%20the%20Gita%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20education%20system%20introduced%20by%20Macaulay%20spawned%20generations%20of%20Indians%20who%20grew%20up%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20inferiority%20about%20their%20own%20culture%20and%20traditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Maharshi%20Dayanand%20Saraswati%20and%20Swami%20Darshananand%20established%20institutions%20like%20%3Cem%3E'gurukuls'%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20carry%20forward%20India's%20traditional%20system%20of%20education%20and%20restore%20its%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20praised%20Yoga%20Guru%20Ramdev%20for%20his%20efforts%20to%20revive%20the%20institution%20established%20by%20Swami%20Darshananand%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Patanjali%20Gurukulam%20saying%20a%20new%20India%20needed%20new%20%3Cem%3E'gurukulams'%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20combined%20traditional%20education%20with%20emerging%20and%20cutting-edge%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20Ramdev%20for%20popularising%20Yoga%2C%20the%20ancient%20Indian%20discipline%20of%20physical%20and%20mental%20well-being%2C%20not%20only%20in%20the%20country%20but%20also%20abroad%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20an%20exemplary%20service%20to%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20can%20be%20seen%20performing%20yogic%20kriyas%20not%20only%20in%20parks%20but%20also%20in%20buses%2C%20trains%2C%20metros%20and%20flights.%20This%20is%20a%20result%20of%20Baba%20Ramdev's%20relentless%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20efforts%20behind%20the%20proclamation%20of%20June%2021%20by%20the%20UN%20as%20the%20International%20Yoga%20Day.%20The%20Union%20minister%20said%20the%20journey%20of%20Ramdev%20and%20Acharya%20Balkrishna%20from%20their%20humble%20beginnings%20to%20the%20height%20of%20their%20achievements%20at%20present%20is%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration%20to%20the%20whole%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20urged%20them%20to%20do%20something%20about%20the%20revival%20of%20Sanskrit%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20scientific%20language%20but%20the%20number%20of%20people%20capable%20of%20speaking%20and%20writing%20it%20is%20increasingly%20getting%20smaller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Uttarakhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%2C%20his%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20counterpart%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20BJP%20spokesman%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20participated%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehavan%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20Jwalapur%20Mahavidyalaya%20ground%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20Patanjali%20Gurukulam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20during%20the%20programme%2C%20Mr%20Dhami%20said%20the%20country%20is%20getting%20rid%20of%20its%20slave%20mentality%20under%20the%20dynamic%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20is%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20January%2022%20when%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20will%20take%20place.%20There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20the%20joy%20of%20Ram%20devotees%20and%20those%20who%20love%20this%20country%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20Mr%20Trivedi%20said%20a%20new%20India%20which%20takes%20pride%20in%20itself%2C%20in%20its%20own%20traditions%20and%20cultural%20symbols%20is%20emerging%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20students%20of%20Patanjali%20Yogpeeth%20attending%20the%20ceremony%2C%20Mr%20Trivedi%20said%20India%20is%20the%20youngest%20country%20in%20the%20world%20but%20the%20oldest%20civilisation%20and%20he%20can%20see%20the%20combination%20of%20the%20two%20in%20the%20precincts%20of%20the%20gurukul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20combination%20here%2C%20I%20can%20see%20the%20seeds%20of%20India's%20great%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Meghwal%20showered%20praise%20on%20PM%20Modi%20for%20the%20passage%20of%20legislation%20in%20Parliament%20which%20would%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20with%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20