0a%20history%20of%20seizures%20and%20her%20brain%20MRI%20was%20done%20which%20showed%20a%20tumour%20in%20the%20left%20side%20of%20her%20brain%20adjacent%20to%20speech%2Flanguage%20area%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surgery%20lasted%20three%20hours%2C%20including%20time%20taken%20for%20giving%20local%20anaesthesia%20to%20the%20child%20by%20neuroanaesthetists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tumour%20was%20removed%20successfully%20by%20a%20team%20of%20neurosurgeons%20as%20she%20remained%20conscious%20throughout%20the%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnological%20adjuncts%20viz%20preoperative%20functional%20MRI%20brain%2C%20intraoperative%20ultrasonography%2C%20neuronavigation%20were%20used%20to%20localise%20tumour%20precisely%20during%20resection%20while%20mapping%20of%20functional%20areas%20was%20being%20carried%20out%20under%20awake%20conditions.%20Ice%20cold%20saline%20was%20used%20for%20the%20brain%20surface%20to%20prevent%20any%20seizures%20during%20the%20procedure%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20child%20is%20doing%20well%20and%20will%20be%20sent%20home%20on%20Monday%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20long%20discussion%20was%20held%20between%20team%20members%2C%20patient's%20family%20and%20the%20child%20before%20taking%20a%20decision%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20surgery.%20They%20were%20counselled%20at%20length%20on%20steps%20of%20procedure%2C%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20shown%20common%20objects%2C%20common%20animals%20and%20given%20some%20tasks%20for%20language%20and%20sensorimotor%20assessments%20before%20surgery%2C%20which%20were%20repeated%20during%20the%20surgical%20procedure%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20a%20first%20standard%20student%20and%20was%20quick%20in%20identifying%20the%20picture%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20surgery%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAwake%20surgeries%20for%20brain%20tumours%20are%20done%20for%20maximising%20tumour%20removals%20and%20minimising%20neurological%20deficits%20usually.%20During%20awake%20craniotomy%2C%20patients%20should%20feel%20a%20minimum%20level%20of%20pain%20while%20being%20completely%20able%20to%20cooperate%20in%20neurological%20tests%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20this%20method%20is%20called%20awake%20craniotomy%2C%20this%20method%20requires%20even%20more%20collaboration%20in%20perfect%20harmony%20of%20the%20surgical%20and%20anaesthesia%20teams%20than%20other%20operations%20under%20general%20anaesthesia%20said%2C''%20Dr%20Deepak%20Gupta%2C%20Professor%20of%20Neurosurgery%20who%20performed%20this%20operation%20with%20his%20team%20with%20neuroanesthesia%20team%20led%20by%20Dr%20Mihir%20Pandia%20and%20Dr%20Gyanendra%20Pal%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAkshita%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20youngest%20child%20in%20the%20world%20to%20undergo%20successful%20brain%20tumour%20surgery%20under%20awake%20conditions%20at%20this%20age%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Gupta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704562020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdgjn3418_child-1200-_625x300_06_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-year-old-youngest-in-world-to-undergo-successful-awake-brain-surgery-4812441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20Delhi%2C%20successfully%20performed%20a%20brain%20tumour%20surgery%20on%20a%20five-year-old%20girl%20while%20keeping%20her%20in%20a%20conscious%20state%20during%20the%20operation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-year-old-youngest-in-world-to-undergo-successful-awake-brain-surgery-4812441%2