E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F01%2Fman-strips-naked-jumps-into-bass-pro-shops-leeds-aquarium-and-knocks-himself-unconscious.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVideo%20taken%20by%20bystanders%20showed%20the%20man%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Bcannonball%26quot%3B%20dive%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Einto%20the%20aquarium%20and%20later%20stand%20under%20the%20waterfall%2C%20reported%20AL.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIrwin%20noted%20that%20the%20man%20spent%20about%20five%20minutes%20in%20the%20water%20before%20officers%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20exited%20the%20water%20to%20confront%20two%20police%20officers%2C%20only%20to%20dive%20back%20into%20the%20aquarium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvedntually%2C%20the%20man%20climbed%20over%20the%20side%20of%20the%20aquarium%2C%20falling%20to%20the%20concrete%20floor%20below%2C%20where%20he%20appeared%20unconscious%2C%20said%20AL.com.%20Law%20enforcement%20swiftly%20apprehended%20him%20and%20handcuffed%20the%20naked%20man%2C%20who%2C%20when%20he%20regained%20consciousness%2C%20started%20to%20struggle%20with%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20charged%20with%20public%20lewdness%2C%20disorderly%20conduct%2C%20resisting%20arrest%2C%20assault%20on%20police%2C%20two%20counts%20of%20criminal%20mischief%2C%20and%20two%20counts%20of%20reckless%20endangerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20Chief%20Irwin%20said%20the%20man%20suffered%20from%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20according%20to%20his%20family%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3EWAFF%2048%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20contacted%20the%20Leeds%20Alabama%20Police%20Department%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falabama-man-arrested-diving-into-bass-pro-shop-nude-202%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704559532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65997fcf6979d73718211125%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falabama-man-arrested-diving-into-bass-pro-shop-nude-202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20was%20arrested%20in%20Leeds%2C%20Alabama%2C%20on%20multiple%20charges%20after%20plunging%20into%20a%20Bass%20Pro%20aquarium%20naked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A145%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falabama-man-arrested-diving-into-bass-pro-shop-nude-202%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Hope%2C%20Better%20To%20Die%20In%20Jail%26quot%3B%3A%20Naresh%20Goyal%20To%20Court%20With%20Folded%20Hands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJet%20Airways%20founder%20Naresh%20Goyal%2C%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20alleged%20fraud%20of%20Rs%20538%20crore%20at%20Canara%20Bank%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20told%20a%20special%20court%20here%20with%20%26quot%3Bfolded%20hands%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Blost%20every%20hope%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20if%20he%20dies%20in%20jail%26quot%3B%20than%20living%20in%20his%20present%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20septuagenarian%2C%20who%20turned%20teary-eyed%2C%20submitted%20that%20he%20misses%20his%20wife%20Anita%20very%20badly%20and%20said%20she%20is%20in%20the%20advanced%20stage%20of%20cancer%2C%20according%20to%20court%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20arrested%20Goyal%20on%20September%201%20last%20year%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20bank%20fraud.%20He%20is%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20at%20Arthur%20Road%20jail%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20had%20moved%20a%20bail%20application%20before%20special%20judge%20M%20G%20Desphande.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20produced%20before%20the%20court%20on%20Saturday%20and%20during%20the%20proceedings%20Mr%20Goyal%20requested%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20personal%20hearing%2C%20which%20the%20judge%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20court's%20'roznama'%20(record%20of%20daily%20hearings)%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20with%20folded%20hands%20and%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%20tremors%20in%20his%20whole%20body%26quot%3B%20submitted%20that%20%26quot%3Bhis%20health%20is%20very%20bad%20and%20precarious%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20businessman%20said%20that%20his%20wife%20is%20bedridden%20and%20their%20only%20daughter%20too%20is%20unwell.%20The%20jail%20staff%20has%20their%20limitations%20in%20helping%20him%2C%20said%20Mr%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20him%20patiently%20and%20also%20observed%20him%20when%20he%20made%20the%20submissions%20as%20such.%20I%20found%20that%20his%20whole%20body%20was%20trembling.%20He%20needs%20assistance%20even%20to%20stand%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20pointed%20to%20his%20knees%20and%20said%20they%20were%20swollen%20and%20painful%20and%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20fold%20his%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jet%20Airways%20founder%20brought%20to%20the%20court's%20notice%20that%20he%20has%20severe%20pain%20while%20urinating%20and%20sometimes%20blood%20is%20passed%20through%20urine%2C%20coupled%20with%20unsustainable%20pain.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20he%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20get%20assistance%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20businessman%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20he%20had%20become%20very%20weak%20and%20there%20was%20no%20use%20in%20referring%20him%20to%20J%20J%20Hospital.%20The%20journey%20with%20other%20inmates%20as%20per%20the%20convenience%20of%20prison%20staff%20and%20escort%20party%20from%20Arthur%20Road%20jail%20to%20the%20hospital%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20troublesome%2C%20hectic%20and%20tedious%20which%20he%20cannot%20bear%20and%20sustain%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20there%20is%20always%20a%20long%20queue%20of%20patients%20and%20he%20cannot%20reach%20the%20doctor%20in%20time%20and%20whenever%20he%20is%20examined%20by%20the%20doctor%20further%20follow-up%20is%20not%20possible%2C%20Goyal%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Goyal%20said%20that%20these%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20badly%20affecting%20his%20health%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20wife%20Anita%20is%20in%20the%20advanced%20stage%20of%20cancer%20and%20undergoing%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20one%20to%20look%20after%20her%20as%20his%20only%20daughter%20is%20also%20suffering%20from%20health%20issues%2C%20submitted%20Goyal%2C%20with%20tears%20in%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20requested%20the%20court%20not%20to%20send%20him%20to%20J%20J%20Hospital%20and%20instead%20%26quot%3Ballow%20him%20to%20die%20in%20the%20jail%20itself%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20has%20lost%20every%20hope%20of%20life%20and%20(it's)%20better%20he%20should%20die%20rather%20than%20be%20alive%20in%20such%20a%20situation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20submitted%20that%20he%20would%20turn%2075%20and%20he%20has%20no%20hope%20for%20any%20future.%20It's%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20if%20he%20dies%20in%20jail%2C%20his%20destiny%20would%20rescue%20him%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20also%20submitted%20that%20his%20health%20doesn't%20permit%20him%20to%20attend%20the%20court%20personally.%20This%20time%2C%20Goyal%20said%2C%20he%20insisted%20that%20he%20be%20produced%20before%20the%20court%20so%20that%20he%20would%20be%20able%20to%20submit%20everything%20personally.%20He%20said%20he%20won't%20insist%20on%20physical%20appearance%20any%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20everything%20he%20has%20submitted%20and%20also%20assured%20the%20accused%20that%20he%20will%20not%20be%20left%20helpless%20and%20all%20possible%20care%20of%20his%20mental%20and%20physical%20health%20will%20be%20taken%20with%20proper%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said%20after%20hearing%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%