%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20the%20series%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20be%20surveying%20India%E2%80%99s%20long%20and%20exciting%20churn%20of%20cultural%20ideas%2C%20beliefs%2C%20and%20values%E2%80%94some%20that%20still%20shape%20us%20today%2C%20and%20others%20that%20have%20been%20lost%20forever.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20dwell%20much%20on%20boring%20dates%2C%20battles%2C%20and%20kings%E2%80%94the%20sort%20of%20stuff%20that%20turned%20you%20off%20history%20in%20school.%20Instead%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20explore%20the%20roots%20and%20the%20evolution%20of%20deeper%20cultural%20and%20social%20currents%20that%20have%20made%20us%20who%20we%20are%2C%20using%20carefully%20curated%20visuals%20to%20illustrate%20my%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20series%20mostly%20mirrors%20%E2%80%93%20and%20often%20extends%20%E2%80%93%20the%20contents%20of%20my%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndians%3A%20A%20Brief%20History%20of%20a%20Civilization%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Penguin%20India%2C%202021).%20For%20both%20the%20book%20and%20the%20series%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20leaned%20on%20diverse%20academic%20scholarship%20as%20well%20as%20primary%20sources%E2%80%94from%20archaeologists%E2%80%99%20site%20reports%20to%20travellers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20to%20archaeogenetic%20research.%20My%20hope%20is%20to%20advance%20a%20fresh%20understanding%20of%20our%20past%20that%E2%80%99s%20rooted%20in%20sound%20scholarship%2C%20while%20illuminating%20some%20of%20the%20most%20consequential%20trends%2C%20transformations%20and%20fault%20lines%20of%20Indian%20civilisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20also%20be%20discussing%20some%20of%20the%20most%20polarising%20topics%20of%20our%20history%20today.%20Questions%20li