lped%20the%20country%20make%20remarkable%20achievements%20in%20various%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20Aadhaar....because%20we%20have%20bank%20accounts.%20By%20having%20bank%20accounts%20we%20have%20changed%20not%20only%20governance%20but%20also%20society.%20By%20connecting%20it%20to%20the%20phone%2C%20we%20have%20ensured%20direct%20benefits.%20So%20we%20have%20used%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20government%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20done%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20work%26quot%3B%20to%20change%20India%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20work%20is%20to%20be%20continued%2C%20we%20have%20to%20create%20'Viksit%20Bharat%2C'%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20problems%20that%20Indians%20encounter%20like%20health%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20house%2C%20education%20and%20so%20on%2C%20are%20the%20same%20in%20many%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20developed%20world%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20only%20India's%20problems...they%20are%20everybody's%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20even%20a%20problem%20in%20the%20developed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20said%20he%20was%20finishing%2046%20years%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20the%20last%2010%20years%20for%20me%2C%20five%20years%20as%20a%20minister%20and%20five%20years%20before%20that%2C%20have%20been%20actually%20the%20most%20satisfying%20years%2C%20for%20me.%20Because%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20a%20complete%20change%20in%20how%20the%20government%20performs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%20is%20more%20sensitive%20and%20bankers%20are%20more%20friendly%20towards%20the%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20V%20Muraleedhar