5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20an%20uphill%20battle%20is%20no%20rocket%20science%20but%20the%20Sebi-Adani-Hindenburg%20verdict%20has%20lent%20a%20moral%20urgency%20to%20the%20task.%20After%20this%20judgment%20the%20democratic%20forces%20can%20no%20longer%20hope%20to%20look%20to%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20for%20any%20kind%20of%20solace%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20or%20EVMs.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20level%20playing%20field%20in%20the%202024%20contest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3EUndoubtedly%20the%20strategic%20and%20overarching%20objective%20of%20the%202024%20battle%20is%20a%20comprehensive%20defeat%20for%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%3B%20but%20to%20achieve%20that%20goal%20it%20would%20be%20necessary%20to%20understand%20%E2%80%93%20and%20deal%20with%20%E2%80%93%20the%20nature%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20staying%20power.%20It%20is%20easy%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20political%20rivals%20to%20underestimate%20the%20elements%20of%20his%20acceptability%3B%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20particularly%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20has%20been%20spectacularly%20dismissive%20of%20his%20seemingly%20unfading%20appeal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20recognised%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20answers%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20basic%20urge%20for%20a%20stable%20political%20and%20governmental%20arrangement.%20He%20also%20has%20come%20to%20satisfy%20most%20citizens%E2%80%99%20native%20desire%20to%20feel%20they%20live%20in%20a%20strong%20and%20safe%20India.%20It%20is%20possible%20to%20quibble%20with%20the%20Modi%20regime%E2%80%99s%20tall%20claims%20in%20matters%20of%20defence%20and%20internal%20security%20%E2%80%93%20most%20Indians%20are%20aware%20of%20uncertainties%20and%20hostilities%20that%20define%20the%20external%20landscape%20%E2%80%93%20and%20those%20who%20feel%20the%20imperative%20to%20replace%20Modi%20would%20have%20to%20tweak%20their%20appeal%20and%20argument%20to%20address%20these%20two%20fundamental%20concerns%20of%20stability%20and%20safety.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20means%2C%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20must%20necessarily%20demonstrate%20a%20capacity%20and%20willingness%20to%20act%20collectively%20and%20coherently%20as%20they%20gird%20up%20for%20the%20battle.%20Egos%20and%20ambitions%2C%20of%20course%2C%20cannot%20be%20wished%20away%20but%20cannot%20be%20coddled%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20grand%20objective%20%E2%80%93%20a%20comprehensive%20defeat%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20primary%20responsibility%20in%20this%20endeavour%20rests%20with%20the%20Congress%20party.%20Its%20leadership%20must%20understand%20and%20accept%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20not%20be%20acceptable%20as%20a%20prime%20ministerial%20face%3B%20nor%20will%20country%20want%20to%20countenance%20a%20Manmohan%20Singh%20type%20of%20arrangement%20where%20the%20Gandhis%20would%20continue%20to%20call%20the%20shots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-what-the-congress-must-do-now-to-quickly-reset-the-2024-chessboard%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20What%20the%20Congress%20Must%20Do%20Now%20to%20Quickly%20Reset%20the%202024%20Chessboard%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20equal%20onus%20is%20on%20the%20non-Congress%20partners%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20The%20alliance%20leaders%20need%20to%20help%20the%20Congress%20deal%20with%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20conundrum.%20The%20Gandhis%E2%80%99%20primacy%20in%20the%20Congress%20is%20not%20open%20to%20any%20challenge%20in%20the%20short%20time%20before%20the%20election.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20unstated%20tactical%20requirement%20will%20be%20to%20ensure%20that%20Modi%20does%20not%20have%20the%20Gandhis%20as%20the%20punching%20bag.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20ensured%20that%20the%20Gandhis%20and%20their%20mixed%20baggage%20do%20not%20distract%20from%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20principal%20charge%20against%20the%20BJP%3A%20that%2010%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20have%20produced%20an%20unequal%2C%20unfair%2C%20unsafe%2C%20unfree%20and%20un-harmonious%20social%20order.%20Modi%20would%20once%20again%20want%20to%20make%20the%20election%20about%20the%20Gandhis%2C%20whereas%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20make%20it%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20far-from-shining%20record.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20Modi%20has%20been%20allowed%20a%20free%20pass.%20If%20things%20have%20gone%20wrong%2C%20if%20the%20promises%20have%20not%20been%20kept%2C%20if%20the%20criminals%20and%20crooks%20have%20not%20been%20brought%20to%20heel%2C%20if%20the%20Chinese%20have%20encroached%20in%20territories%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdays-after-china-renames-places-in-arunachal-amit-shah-says-not-an-inch-of-land-can-be-encroached%5C%22%3Epreviously%20under%20our%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20black%20money%20has%20made%20a%20triumphant%20return%2C%20if%20terrorists%20continue%20to%20target%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjammu-kashmir-militant-rajouri-encounter-four-soldiers-army-killed%5C%22%3Earmy%20officers%20in%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20if%20Manipur%20continues%20to%20simmer%20with%20tension%20and%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20someone%20else%E2%80%99%20fault.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20after%2010%20years%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20apologists%20continue%20to%20harp%20on%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cblunders.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20This%20bluff%20needs%20to%20be%20called.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20leaders%20have%20the%20rhetorical%20skills%2C%20the%20idiom%2C%20the%20local%20flavour%2C%20acumen%2C%20street-smartness%20and%20a%20political%20grammar%20of%20their%20own%2C%20and%20are%20therefore%20well-equipped%20to%20nail%20the%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20exaggerated%20claims.%20The%20mythology%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20development%20has%20to%20be%20de-mystified%20in%20village%20by%20village%2C%20qasba%20by%20qasba.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20leaders%20will%20need%20to%20devise%20a%20narrative%20that%20taps%20the%20vast%20masses%E2%80%99%20grievances%20and%20disappointments%3B%20only%20then%C2%A0%20can%C2%A0%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20trump%20card%20%E2%80%93%20Hindutva%2FAyodhya%20temple%20%E2%80%93%20be%20neutralised.%20A%20national%20election%20is%20the%20only%20time%20when%20everyone%20gets%20a%20chance%20to%20articulate%20their%20promise%20of%20firm%20and%20fair%20governance.%20The%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20to%20spell%20out%20its%20ideas%20of%20%E2%80%9Cno%20appeasement%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20neither%20of%20the%20Hindus%20nor%20of%20the%20Muslims.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20trick%20is%20to%20make%20the%20Hindus%20feel%20that%20being%20fair%20towards%20the%20Muslims%20does%20not%20mean%20being%20unfair%20towards%20the%20majority%20community.%20The%20crux%20is%20to%20make%20the%20Hindus%20snap%20out%20of%20the%20stupor%20that%20nine%20decade%E2%80%99s%20of%20fear-mongering%20from%20Nagpur%20has%20produced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20inevitable%20about%20a%20third%20term%20for%20Modi.%20He%20is%20neither%20invincible%20nor%20unstoppable.%20He%20has%20never%20won%20a%20majority%20of%20votes%2C%20and%2C%20it%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpresent%20and%20clear%E2%80%9D%20duty%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20to%20gather%20together%20the%20non-Modi%20majority.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%20not%20an%20insurmountable%20task.%20What%20it%20needs%20is%20for%20the%20country%20to%20be%20assured%20that%20a%20collective%20coalition%20arrangement%20can%20be%20effectively%20purposeful%2C%20competent%20as%20well%20as%20compassionate%20in%20producing%20stability%2C%20security%20and%20firm%20and%20fair%20governance.%20The%20country%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20a%20clear-cut%20choice%20between%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20coalition%20of%20vested%20interests%20and%20bigotry%20and%20an%20India%20that%20belongs%20to%20all%20and%20whose%20society%20is%20not%20perpetually%20at%20war%20against%20enemies%20within%20and%20out.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704536464000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06124906%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-india-alliance-rahul-gandhi-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20this%20year%20are%20about%20sab%20ka%20INDIA%20versus%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20coalition%20of%20vested%20interests%20and%20bigotry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-india-alliance-rahul-gandhi-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Vibrant%20Gujarat%20summits%20helped%20state%20get%20%2455%20bn%20FDI%20in%20two%20decades'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704535437000%2C%22visual%22%3A