%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20robbery%20also%2C%20sir.%20Plus%20there%20is%20a%20deep%20wound%20from%20a%20heavy%20object%20on%20the%20forehead.%20Chances%20are%20there%20was%20some%20foul%20play%2C%20but%20post-mortem%20report%20is%20still%20awaited%E2%80%99%2C%20continued%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20own%20steam%20iron%20was%20used%2C%20sir.%20There%20is%20some%20blood%20on%20the%20iron%E2%80%9D%2C%20Constable%20Rana%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20much%20money%20was%20taken%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoney%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20sir%E2%80%9D%2C%20mumbled%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20much%20money%20was%20stolen!%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20the%20cause%20of%20death%2C%20whether%20at%20all%20it%20was%20murder%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20enquiry%20are%20you%20doing%3F%20This%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20do%20proper%20tafteesh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20looked%20down%20at%20his%20feet%2C%20while%20Constable%20Rana%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20we%20know%20that%20a%20pateela%20of%20cooked%20meat%20was%20stolen%20from%20the%20kitchen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCooked%20meat!%E2%80%9D%20the%20ACP%20looked%20shocked.%20%E2%80%9CTotal%20scoundrels!%20People%20have%20started%20to%20kill%20for%20meat%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shook%20his%20head%20in%20disbelief.%20%E2%80%9CAnyway%2C%20then%20it%20must%20be%20an%20internal%20community%20matter%20only%20%E2%80%93%20for%20cooked%20meat%2C%20just%20imagine.%E2%80%9D%20He%20sucked%20at%20the%20dregs%20in%20the%20tetra%20pack%2C%20examined%20it%20once%20and%20then%20put%20it%20back%20on%20the%20table.%20%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20have!%E2%80%9D%20he%20pushed%20the%20remaining%20lassi%20packets%20towards%20the%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHmm%2C%20have%20you%20seized%20the%20raw%20meat%20in%20their%20fridge%20for%20further%20examination%3F%20Do%20they%20even%20keep%20a%20fridge%2C%20or%20leave%20the%20meat%20outside%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20what%20connection%20would%20that%20have%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20began%20tentatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20must%20investigate%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20case.%20And%20nature%20of%20meat%20has%20direct%20bearing%3A%20if%20it%20is%20beef%2C%20then%20you%20immediately%20know%20that%20a%20particular%20community%2C%20which%20consumes%20that%20meat%2C%20is%20responsible.%20Send%20samples%20for%20analysis%20immediately.%20In%20fact%2C%20take%20samples%20from%20that%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20shop%20also.%20That%20gali%20has%20become%20a%20sensitive%20area%20%E2%80%93%20we%20must%20keep%20ourselves%20fully%20informed%20about%20what%20goes%20on%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20coughed%20delicately.%20%E2%80%98Sir%2C%20if%20it%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20beef%2C%20it%20might%20get%20complicated.%20There%20are%20some%20youth%20in%20the%20area%2C%20who%20have%20formed%20a%20sena.%20In%20fact%2C%20Rana%20took%20one%20of%20them%20to%20Rahman%20ji%E2%80%99s%20shop%20late%20last%20night.%20I%20would%20not%20have%20brought%20it%20up%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20I%20must%20inform%20you%2C%20sir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20looked%20very%20surprised%20that%20Achche%20Lal%20was%20aware.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20true%2C%20Rana%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20ACP%20asked%20sternly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20I%20went%20for%20dinner%2C%20sir.%20After%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTook%20your%20activist%20friend%20also%3F%20Rana%20you%20have%20to%20stop%20acting%20like%20some%20hero.%20You%E2%80%99re%20in%20service%20now.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20formal%20complaints%2C%20or%20I%20will%20have%20to%20take%20action%20against%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20those%20YouTube%20videos%20that%20you%20watch%20colour%20your%20views%20and%20make%20you%20very%20casual%2C%20Rana%E2%80%9D%2C%20added%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20agree.%20You%20must%20be%20neutral%20in%20your%20approach.%20Duty%20comes%20first%20before%20anything%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20ACP.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20at%20least%20one%20good%20thing%20has%20happened.%20We%20can%20rest%20assured%20that%20the%20Sena%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20because%20that%20fellow%20was%20in%20Rana%E2%80%99s%20sight%20all%20evening.%20Correct%20Rana%3F%20Now!%20What%20other%20angles%20need%20investigation%3F%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20call%20this%20Jamal%20for%20questioning%3F%20I%20have%20been%20wanting%20to%20talk%20to%20him%3B%20lately%20he%20has%20become%20too%20rough.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20Jamal%20got%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%20Sir%3F%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%E2%80%99s%20jaws%20tightened%20and%20his%20voice%20rose%20a%20notch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20may%20be%20a%20wider%20conspiracy.%20How%20will%20we%20find%20out%20unless%20we%20do%20proper%20investigation%3F%20The%20government%20has%20now%20made%20it%20very%20difficult%20for%20foreign%20funds%20to%20reach%20these%20protestors.%20Who%20knows%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20they%20are%20committing%20robberies%20now%20to%20fund%20the%20anti-India%20eco-system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSir%2C%20there%20is%20his%20friend%20also%2C%20Habib%E2%80%9D%2C%20added%20Rana%20helpfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACP%20stretched%20his%20feet%20out%20and%20adjusted%20the%20rod%20heater.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20Habib%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20student%2C%20sir.%20He%20is%20writing%20a%20detective%20novel%20it%20seems.%20Has%20met%20me%20several%20times%20to%20ask%20for%20ideas%20for%20his%20novel.%20He%20is%20not%20a%20bad%20boy%2C%20sir%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Achche%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20tried%20to%20create%20obstruction%20once%2C%20sir.%20I%20gave%20him%20one%20tight%20slap%E2%80%9D%2C%20countered%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20Mullah%20detective!%E2%80%9D%20chortled%20the%20ACP.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20his%20plot%20line%20he%20wants%20to%20take%20from%20the%20police%3F%20Bring%20him%20in.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20meet%20him.%20And%20listen%2C%20before%20we%20finish%20this%20meeting%2C%20what%20about%20training%20programme%20for%20our%20new%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%3F%20Do%20you%20know%20the%20new%20sections%3F%20Section%20302%20is%20not%20murder%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20merely%20%E2%80%98snatching%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20new%20criminal%20law.%20When%20it%20comes%20into%20force%2C%20be%20careful%20while%20registering%20FIRs.%20Give%20correct%20section%20numbers.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20convert%20murder%20into%20a%20snatching%20crime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Awdhesh%20Rana%20was%20out%20to%20do%20tafteesh%2C%20but%20he%20felt%20moody%20and%20irritable.%20%E2%80%9CNobody%20can%20be%20trusted%20with%20even%20a%20harmless%20secret%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%20As%20he%20rode%20past%20Bhawani%20Mishthan%20Bhandar%2C%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20waved%20to%20him.%20It%20annoyed%20Constable%20Rana%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20on%20duty%20now%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20called%20out%20tersely.%20%E2%80%98Everyone%20just%20wants%20to%20be%20seen%20with%20me%2C%20and%20then%20I%20get%20into%20trouble%20with%20my%20superiors%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20thought%20to%20himself%20and%20made%20a%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20rode%20straight%20to%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20where%20he%20saw%20the%20two%20brothers%2C%20Arshad%20and%20Abrar%2C%20sitting%20outside%20the%20now%20closed%20Rahmania%20hotel.%20He%20jumped%20off%20his%20motorcycle%2C%20caught%20Arshad%E2%80%99s%20shirtfront%2C%20hauled%20him%20up%20and%20gave%20him%20a%20stinging%20slap%20across%20the%20face.%20%E2%80%9CHaven%E2%80%99t%20I%20told%20you%20to%20not%20hang%20about%20at%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20destroying%20evidence%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20had%20had%20a%20slow%20morning%20with%20no%20work%20left%20to%20do%2C%20and%20nowhere%20else%20to%20go.%20They%20had%20been%20sitting%20on%20the%20parapet%20outside%20Rahmania%2C%20discussing%20their%20prospects%2C%20before%20this%20sudden%20and%20violent%20interruption.%20Arshad%20held%20his%20cheek%20in%20his%20right%20hand%20and%20cried%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20did%20I%20do%2C%20saheb%3F%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20had%20covered%20his%20face%20with%20his%20forearm%2C%20also%20expecting%20a%20blow.%20He%20quietly%20moved%20away%20from%20Rana%E2%80%99s%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDidn%E2%80%99t%20I%20tell%20you%20to%20not%20mention%20that%20I%20had%20visited%20the%20restaurant%3F%20You%20thought%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20know%3F%20Nothing%20will%20happen%20to%20me%2C%20you%20bastard%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99ll%20make%20sure%20your%20name%20comes%20in%20the%20chargesheet.%20Then%20you%20can%20rot%20in%20jail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20Allah%20ki%20qasam%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20your%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20howled.%20%E2%80%9CSomebody%20else%20must%20have%20informed.%20Remember%2C%20that%20loafer%20Salman%20was%20also%20there%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20like%20a%20reasonable%20explanation%20to%20Rana.%20%E2%80%9CHmm%2C%20achcha%3F%20Well%2C%20you%20should%20have%20said%20earlier.%20You%20got%20beaten%20up%20for%20nothing%20then.%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20looked%20almost%20apologetic.%20He%20unlocked%20the%20premises%20and%20led%20them%20inside.%20%E2%80%9CChal%2C%20cigarette%20pila%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20you%20order%20the%20restaurant%20to%20be%20opened%20again%3F%20After%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20nobody%20is%20interested%2C%20but%20how%20will%20we%20survive%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20tell%20me%20in%20great%20detail%20who%20all%20came%20to%20the%20restaurant%20that%20evening%3F%20Who%20said%20what%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20put%20down%20his%20backpack%20and%20conscientiously%20took%20out%20his%20Neelgagan%20notebook.%20He%20wrote%20down%20a%20few%20names%20in%20one%20column%20and%20read%20each%20name%20out%20to%20the%20brothers%3A%20%E2%80%9CDid%20all%20of%20them%20come%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20took%20notes%20against%20each%20name%20as%20Arshad%20and%20Abrar%20tried%20to%20remember%20conversations%20from%20that%20evening.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06122634%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-06-at-11.38.49-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06122634%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-06-at-11.38.49-AM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06122634%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-06-at-11.38.49-AM-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06122634%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-06-at-11.38.49-AM-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691818%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20other%20thing%2C%20how%20much%20money%20was%20stolen%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbrar%20and%20Arshad%20looked%20at%20each%20other.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%2C%20sir.%20Rahman%20miyan%20did%20the%20accounts%20himself.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20how%20much%20money%20was%20in%20the%20cashbox.%20But%20he%20was%20very%20upset%20with%20me%20because%20I%20brought%20Salman%20inside%20while%20the%20almirah%20was%20open%20and%20the%20cash%20box%20was%20visible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20anything%20else%20missing%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rana%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlmirah%20was%20open%20and%20all%20the%20papers%20were%20scattered%2C%20sir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHmm%2C%20now%20I%20have%20to%20seize%20all%20the%20raw%20meat%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Take%20me%20to%20the%20fridge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inspection%20of%20the%20fridge%20revealed%20a%20small%20quantity%20of%20liver%20and%20kidneys%2C%20two%20bottles%20of%20coke%2C%20Lassi%20Tetra%20packs%2C%20eggs%2C%20lemon%20(shriveled%20from%20age)%20and%20dry%20coriander%20leaves.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20mutton%20or%20something%20else%2C%20hain%3F%E2%80%9D%20Asked%20Constable%20Rana%20only%20half-jokingly.%20%E2%80%9CNever%20know%20with%20you%20people.%20One%20love%20jihadi%20had%20cut%20his%20wife%20into%20small%20pieces%20and%20put%20it%20in%20the%20fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPack%20it%20in%20a%20tiffin%20carrier%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20ordered%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaji%20saheb%E2%80%99s%20best%20aluminium%20tiffin%20carrier%20was%20also%20stolen.%20I%20had%20told%20you%20that%20day%20only%2C%20sir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20had%20the%20sample%20put%20in%20two%20double%20layers%20of%20polythene%20and%20then%20put%20it%20in%20the%20outer%20pocket%20of%20his%20backpack%2C%20while%20scrunching%20his%20nose%2C%20and%20holding%20his%20breath.%20He%20then%20left%20the%20brothers%20and%20rode%20up%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20house.%20It%20looked%20like%20a%20house%20in%20mourning%20still%3A%20it%20was%20already%20overcast%20outside%2C%20but%20inside%20was%20positively%20dark.%20All%20the%20curtains%20were%20drawn%2C%20and%20he%20felt%20his%20way%20about%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20electric%20heaters.%20Rahman%20ji%E2%80%99s%20wife%20sat%20in%20the%20drawing%20room%3B%20her%20feet%20propped%20up%20on%20a%20stool%20and%20covered%20in%20soft%20Chinese%20blankets.%20Her%20eyes%20were%20swollen%2C%20and%20her%20face%20red.%20%E2%80%98Madam%20ji%2C%20can%20you%20tell%20me%20how%20much%20cash%20was%20stolen%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs.%20Rahman%20let%20out%20a%20wail%20again.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20would%20I%20know%3F%20He%20took%20care%20of%20everything.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20me%20want%20for%20anything.%20He%20gave%20me%20cash%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20every%20week%20for%20household%20expenses%2C%20or%20whenever%20else%20I%20needed%20it.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20hisab-kitab.%20Beta%2C%20Tauseeeef%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20she%20yelled%20suddenly%20and%20a%20young%20man%20appeared.%20He%20was%20short%20and%20stout%20and%20had%20shoulder%20length%20hair%2C%20streaked%20and%20cut%20in%20the%20now%20outdated%20style%20of%20Salman%20Khan%20in%20Tere%20Naam.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20know%20how%20much%20cash%20your%20uncle%20kept%20at%20the%20restaurant%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20phuphu!%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20joined%20the%20business.%E2%80%9D%20He%20looked%20at%20Rana%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20started%20going%20there%2C%20Inspector%20Saheb.%20All%20this%20happened%20so%20suddenly.%20Now%20I%E2%80%99ll%20never%20be%20able%20to%20run%20that%20place%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99ll%20always%20feel%20my%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20ghost%20lingering.%20They%20said%20there%20was%20too%20much%20blood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20aunt%20started%20to%20howl%20again%20and%20Rana%20quickly%20left%20the%20house.%20%E2%80%9CAye%20joker%2C%20baal%20kata%20ley%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20the%20nephew%20before%20he%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20made%20one%20last%20stop%20on%20his%20way%20out%20of%20the%20alley.%20%E2%80%9COye%20Laadley!%20Hand%20over%20all%20your%20meat%20to%20me%20right%20now!%20I%20have%20orders%20to%20seize%20all%20the%20meat%20in%20your%20hotel%20for%20testing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20rose%20from%20his%20chair%20in%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20be%20continued%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahrukh%20Alam%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20write%20a%20murder%20mystery%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%20She%20has%20written%20versions%20of%20this%20story%20since%202013%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%C2%A0has%20published%20one%20such%20version%20earlier.%20She%20is%20hopeful%20that%20she%E2%80%99ll%20deliver%20a%20complete%20mystery%20this%20time.%20%F0%9F%A4%9E%F0%9F%8F%BB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704529555000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06123131%2FUntitled-design-7.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20WhoDunnIt%3A%20This%20is%20the%20fifth%20part%20of%20a%20serialised%20detective%20story%20by%20Shahrukh%20Alam.%20It%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffiction%2Fa-mood-for-murder-episode-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20Lays%20Down%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20Agenda%2C%20Takes%20on%20'BJP's%20Dry%20Clean%20Factory'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06132418%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20laid%20down%20the%20political%20agenda%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20led%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Saturday%2C%20January%206.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Yatra%20will%20touch%20110%20districts%2C%20100%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20and%20337%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20what%20is%20the%20biggest%20mass%20outreach%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20yatra%20that%20will%20begin%20on%20January%2014%2C%202024%20will%20cover%206%2C700%20kilometres%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Imphal%20to%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Yatra%20will%20raise%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20concerns%20of%20Indians%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said%2C%20while%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20allegedly%20anti-people%20policies%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharge%20said%20while%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20so%20much%20time%20for%20photo%20opportunities%20in%20Lakshadweep%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20had%20time%20to%20visit%20the%20conflict-ridden%20Manipur%20and%20give%20a%20healing%20message%20to%20its%20people.%C2%A0%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20be%20a%20political%20platform%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20only%20convey%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20message%20to%20people%2C%20but%20also%20to%20hear%20their%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsecond-avatar-criminal-law-bills-has-anything-changed%5C%22%3Ecriminal%20bills%20which%20were%20passed%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20discussions%20have%20taken%20away%20the%20rights%20of%20labourers.%20The%20union%20government%20has%20tweaked%20the%20laws%20so%20that%20the%20working%20people%20become%20bonded%20labour%20and%20completely%20dependent%20on%20the%20whims%20of%20owners.%20All%20the%20protection%20and%20security%20guaranteed%20to%20the%20working%20people%20of%20the%20country%20before%20and%20after%20independence%20have%20been%20taken%20away%20in%20the%20new%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Yatra%20is%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20fundamental%20concerns%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said%2C%20as%20he%20attacked%20the%20union%20government%20for%20silencing%20the%20opposition%20both%20in%20the%20Parliament%20and%20outside.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20mass%20suspensions%20of%20146%20MPs%2C%20even%20of%20those%20who%20remained%20silent%20or%20were%20seated%20in%20their%20respective%20benches%2C%20from%20both%20the%20Houses%20was%20a%20tactic%20to%20silence%20the%20opposition.%20Outside%20the%20Parliament%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20was%20being%20silenced%20by%20the%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20central%20investigation%20agencies%20against%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20opposition%20party%20cadres%20and%20friends%20and%20relatives%20of%20opposition%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20it%20is%20curious%20that%20agencies%20pursue%20cases%20against%20opposition%20leaders%20only%20until%20they%20are%20in%20opposition%20parties%2C%20but%20conveniently%20stop%20following%20the%20cases%20when%20some%20of%20them%20join%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20leaders%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalankit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(tarnished)%20only%20until%20they%20are%20in%20opposition%20but%20become%20clean%20when%20they%20join%20the%20BJP%20ranks.%20BJP%20is%20running%20a%20dry%20clean%20factory%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20chosen%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20people%20to%20talk%20about%20its%20political%20concerns%20through%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20the%20Congress%20president%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20party%20has%20also%20invited%20INDIA%20parties%20and%20will%20hold%20at%20least%207-8%20big%20rallies%20through%20its%20entire%20run%2C%20apart%20from%20small%20and%20big%20public%20meetings.%20He%20also%20appealed%20to%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20like-minded%20organisations%20to%20join%20the%20yatra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20main%20motivation%20is%20to%20unite%20the%20weaker%20sections%20of%20the%20society%2C%20he%20said%2C%20while%20releasing%20the%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20slogan%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Nyay%20Ka%20Haq%20Milne%20Taq%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20short%20video%20pointing%20out%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20failed%20promises%20like%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99s%20income%2C%20farm%20laws%2C%20and%20two%20crore%20jobs%20every%20year.%20He%20added%20that%20concerns%20like%20the%20rising%20inequality%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20owing%20to%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20crony%20practices%20and%20frequent%20constitutional%20violations%20during%20the%20Modi%20regime%20will%20be%20raised%20aggressively%20during%20the%20Yatra%2C%20and%20appealed%20to%20the%20media%20to%20cover%20the%20Yatra%20widely%20to%20prevent%20any%20further%20backsliding%20of%20democracy%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20party%20has%20also%20appointed%20election%20observers%20in%20500%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20but%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20contest%20after%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20is%20finalised%20with%20the%20INDIA%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704528267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06132418%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress's%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20main%20motivation%20is%20to%20unite%20the%20weaker%20sections%20of%20the%20society%2C%20he%20said%2C%20while%20releasing%20the%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20slogan%2C%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Nyay%20Ka%20Haq%20Milne%20Taq.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Inside%20Alaska%20Airlines%20plane%20after%20part%20blows%20off%20mid-air%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704527479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.c