ndrachud%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20a%20lesson%20learned%20long%20ago%3A%20being%20eloquent%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20you%20are%20an%20honest%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOratory%20is%20an%20art%20and%20one%20can%20be%20an%20expert%20in%20it%2C%20but%20is%20the%20orator%20speaking%20the%20truth%20or%20speaking%20honestly%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20often%20warn%20my%20students%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98debater%E2%80%99.%20There%20is%20no%20education%20on%20the%20ethics%20of%20speech%20in%20debating%20in%20our%20schools.%20A%20speaker%20is%20taught%20to%20be%20able%20to%20argue%20for%20and%20against%20an%20issue%20with%20equal%20eloquence.%20Which%20side%20you%20are%20on%2C%20is%20not%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20side%20is%20important.%20Clever%20speakers%20choose%20sides%20or%20gather%20arguments%20for%20a%20given%20side.%20They%20cannot%20absolve%20themselves%20of%20the%20responsibility%20of%20what%20they%20say%20by%20claiming%20that%20the%20stand%20was%20not%20theirs%2C%20their%20job%20was%20only%20to%20gather%20arguments%20to%20prove%20it%20right.%20We%20know%20that%20they%20have%20chosen%20their%20side.%20The%20debater%20gets%20away%20by%20calling%20it%20an%20inevitability%20of%20his%20profession.%20He%20often%20does%20not%20take%20responsibility%20for%20what%20he%20says%2C%20which%20is%20his%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20answering%20difficult%20questions%20with%20ease.%20There%20were%20questions%20related%20to%20the%20judgement%2C%20he%20was%20part%20of%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-ayodhya-verdict-possession%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNov%252009%252C%25202019-%2CSupreme%2520Court%2527s%2520Ayodhya%2520Verdict%2520Rests%2520on%2520a%2520Glaring%2520Contradiction%2Con%2520%2522balance%2520of%2520probabilities%2522.%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20the%20land%20of%20the%20demolished%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20critical%20question%20was%20why%20the%20judge%20who%20wrote%20the%20decision%20chose%20to%20not%20put%20his%20authorship%20on%20the%20order%2C%20as%20is%20the%20custom.%20In%20response%20to%20this%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20unanimous%20decision%20of%20the%20entire%20bench%2C%20hence%20the%20bench%20decided%20not%20to%20give%20the%20name%20of%20the%20person%20who%20wrote%20it.%20It%20was%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20court%2C%20hence%20no%20need%20for%20the%20name%20of%20the%20person%20who%20voices%20the%20bench.%20But%20his%20explanation%20does%20not%20hold%20because%20this%20is%20not%20and%20has%20not%20been%20the%20tradition%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEXCLUSIVE%20%7C%20VIDEO%3A%20%E2%80%9CSupreme%20Court%20judgement%20on%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20was%20the%20judgement%20of%20the%20court%2C%20not%20any%20individual.%20So%20the%20author%20of%20the%20judgement%20was%20not%20named.%20It%20was%20a%20case%20of%20long%20conflict%20and%20diverse%20viewpoints%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20tells%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PTI_News%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F35820C1DOp%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F35820C1DOp%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1741824258328699387%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnOne%20reason%20for%20the%20author%20not%20giving%20his%20name%20may%20be%20modesty.%20Second%2C%20simple%20cowardice.%20We%20know%20from%20previous%20examples%20that%20you%20cannot%20often%20accuse%20justices%20of%20humility.%20The%20satisfaction%20of%20settling%20such%20a%20vexed%20matter%20of%20historical%20importance%20in%20a%20just%20way%20can%20be%20imagined.%20What%20could%20be%20the%20reason%20for%20restraining%20the%20temptation%20of%20being%20known%20as%20the%20author%20of%20such%20a%20monumental%20judgement%3F%20Or%20did%20our%20judges%20know%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20was%20justifying%20and%20rewarding%20an%20unjust%20act%20and%20did%20not%20want%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20that%3F%20At%20the%20very%20least%2C%20it%20tells%20us%20that%20there%20is%20still%20some%20shame%20left%20in%20our%20elite!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20because%20the%20decision%2C%20as%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20and%20Suhrith%20Parthasarathy%20wrote%2C%20was%20an%20example%20of%20%E2%80%98Matsya%20Nyaya%E2%80%99%3F%20Analysing%20this%20decision%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F930a4c16-3739-4233-8513-5b7b19130cbf%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F930a4c16-3739-4233-8513-5b7b19130cbf%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704603306455000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3tpvz4LpgajRFUzOw0A9dA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejurists%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20it%20is%20based%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%98the%20strong%20shall%20have%20the%20right%20and%20the%20weak%20shall%20have%20to%20suffer%E2%80%99.%20It%20has%20been%20noted%20after%20analysing%20the%20order%20that%20the%20court%20created%20two%20unequal%20sides%20in%20this%20case%20and%20made%20Hindus%20the%20stronger%20side.%20Even%20when%20they%20had%20no%20case%2C%20they%20would%20have%20to%20be%20given%20more%20weight%20than%20the%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20did%20it%20in%20a%20very%20creative%20way.%20First%2C%20it%20declared%20that%20all%20of%20the%202.77%20acres%20of%20land%20on%20which%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20stood%20is%20one%20indivisible%20property.%20Then%20it%20divided%20it%20into%20two%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20the%20inner%20part%20which%20was%20being%20used%20for%20a%20long%20time%20by%20the%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20outer%20part%2C%20which%20was%20separated%20from%20the%20inner%20part%20by%20a%20railing%20after%20Hindus%20committed%20violence%20and%20started%20praying%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Hindus%20had%20been%20laying%20claim%20to%20the%20inner%20part%20of%20the%20mosque%20also%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20including%20through%20acts%20of%20violence%2C%20the%20court%20held%20that%20there%20was%20merit%20in%20their%20claim%20on%20that%20portion%20of%20the%20land.%20Even%20when%20Muslims%20had%20been%20using%20it%20continuously%2C%20the%20consistent%20insistence%20of%20Hindus%20for%20its%20ownership%20made%20the%20site%20disputed.%20But%20since%20the%20Muslims%20did%20not%20insist%20like%20the%20Hindus%20for%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20outer%20part%20of%20the%20mosque%20which%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Hindus%2C%20the%20court%20held%20that%20they%20were%20not%20that%20interested%20in%20that%20part.%20It%20has%20been%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20is%20factually%20wrong.%20Muslims%20did%20keep%20registering%20their%20protest%20from%20time%20to%20time%20even%20if%20they%20did%20not%20do%20it%20forcefully%2C%20that%20is%20violently%2C%20as%20Hindus%20had%20been%20doing.%20Does%20it%20mean%20that%20the%20outer%20part%2C%20which%20again%20was%20only%20a%20part%20of%20the%20whole%2C%20is%20beyond%20any%20dispute%20a%20Hindu%20property%20as%20the%20court%20held%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1-300x205.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F19130137%2Fadmin-ajax-1.v1-1024x699.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22819%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992.%20Photo%3A%20Sanjay%20Sharma%2FINDIAPIX%20NETWORK%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20funny%20and%20dangerous%20argument%20that%20since%20the%20Hindus%20kept%20offering%20worship%20with%20their%20faces%20turned%20towards%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20they%20had%20some%20right%20over%20it.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Muslims%20were%20not%20praying%20looking%20towards%20the%20outer%20side.%20That%20meant%20that%20they%20could%20not%20claim%20it.%20It%20has%20been%20pointed%20out%20that%20Muslims%20could%20not%20have%20kept%20their%20faces%20turned%20towards%20the%20outer%20side%20as%20they%20pray%20with%20their%20faces%20turned%20towards%20Kaaba.%20Is%20this%20how%20you%20create%20rights%20of%20possession%3F%20I%20remember%20a%20jurist%20friend%20chuckling%20that%20if%20this%20argument%20is%20taken%20to%20its%20logical%20conclusion%2C%20all%20the%20properties%20lying%20between%20a%20praying%20Muslim%20and%20the%20Kaaba%20would%20have%20to%20be%20surrendered%20to%20him!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20with%20its%20arguments%2C%20created%20two%20unequal%20parties%20and%20gave%20more%20weight%20to%20Hindus%20than%20Muslims.%20Despite%20accepting%20that%20smuggling%20Hindu%20idols%20into%20a%20mosque%20in%201949%20and%20demolishing%20the%20mosque%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%20were%20criminal%20acts%2C%20the%20court%20handed%20over%20the%20land%20to%20those%20who%20had%20committed%20these%20crimes.%20But%20if%20we%20follow%20the%20logic%20of%20the%20court%2C%20these%20two%20crimes%20should%20also%20be%20considered%20as%20examples%20of%20Hindus%E2%80%99%20deep%20interest%20in%20the%20mosque.%20Through%20these%2C%20Hindus%20were%20trying%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20loved%20this%20place%20so%20much%20that%20they%20could%20commit%20crimes%20repeatedly%20to%20annex%20it.%20The%20court%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20Hindus%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20the%20mosque%20land%20and%20decided%20that%20their%20claim%20was%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThinking%20about%20it%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20I%20wonder%20if%20Israel%20should%20ask%20our%20CJI%20to%20argue%20its%20case%20before%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20to%20prove%20that%20its%20violence%20is%20in%20fact%20the%20demonstration%20of%20its%20love%20for%20the%20land%2C%20and%20since%20it%20has%20never%20ceased%20its%20violence%2C%20it%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20deeply%20interested%20in%20it%20and%20the%20land%20of%20Palestine%20should%20be%20given%20to%20Israel%20as%20it%20has%20proven%20its%20rights%20of%20possession%2C%20and%20the%20Palestinians%20should%20be%20given%20an%20alternative%20piece%20of%20land%20to%20build%20themselves%20as%20a%20nation.%20The%20five-acre%20justice!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20this%2C%20despite%20repeatedly%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20not%20giving%20its%20decision%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20faith%20and%20belief%20of%20any%20community%2C%20ultimately%20it%20decided%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20manufactured%20faith%20of%20Hindus.%20The%20faith%20is%20that%20this%20land%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Ram.%20The%20weight%20of%20this%20faith%20was%20considered%20greater%20than%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20was%20a%20living%20mosque%20there%20and%20Muslims%20were%20worshipping%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20wanted%20us%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20court%20was%20driven%20by%20the%20pious%20intent%20of%20creating%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20country.%20If%20it%20means%20appeasing%20the%20strong%20who%20can%20keep%20committing%20crime%20and%20violence%2C%20one%20should%20do%20it%20by%20manufacturing%20honourable%20arguments%20for%20his%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20the%20case%20was%20very%20old%2C%20long%20and%20complicated%20and%20he%20was%20satisfied%20that%20he%20had%20brought%20it%20to%20a%20conclusion.%20But%20the%20question%20remains%20whether%20this%20decision%20was%20able%20to%20do%20justice.%20And%20did%20it%20calm%20the%20turbulent%20waters%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photograph%20of%20the%20five%20judges%20locking%20their%20hands%20and%20celebrating%20their%20act%20that%20very%20night%20tells%20you%20about%20their%20minds.%20It%20will%20remain%20the%20most%20obnoxious%20image%20of%20our%20judiciary.%20What%20should%20have%20been%20a%20sombre%20moment%20of%20introspection%20for%20them%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20celebration!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20wanted%2C%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20justice%2C%20peace%20for%20the%20nation.%20What%20about%20that%3F%20We%20know%20the%20answer.%20After%20handing%20over%20the%20land%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20to%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20parents%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%2C%20again%20deploying%20his%20creativity%2C%20has%20made%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20a%20disputed%20site.%20He%20did%20it%20by%20inventing%20a%20jurisprudence%20of%20curiosity.%20He%20argued%20that%20someone%20might%20be%20genuinely%20curious%20to%20know%20what%20was%20inside%20the%20mosque.%20It%20is%20their%20right%20to%20satisfy%20this%20curiosity.%20Hence%2C%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20could%20be%20surveyed%20to%20know%20what%20was%20inside%20it.%20It%20did%20not%20mean%20changing%20its%20title.%20But%20the%20mosque%20has%20already%2C%20for%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20lost%20a%20part%20of%20its%20premises%20after%20Hindus%20started%20claiming%20that%20they%20had%20found%20a%20shivling%20during%20the%20survey.%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20was%20inclined%20to%20name%20the%20object%20a%20shivling.%20It%20was%20the%20sober%2C%20persistent%20argument%20of%20the%20lawyer%20of%20the%20masjid%20committee%20which%20forced%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20to%20desist%20from%20doing%20it.%20But%20that%20part%2C%20which%20is%20the%20Wazoo%20Khana%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20was%20sealed%20and%20is%20now%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20worshippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-kashi-vishwanath-gyanvapi-equation-a-parable-for-people-power-politics%5C%22%3EThe%20Kashi%20Vishwanath-Gyanvapi%20Equation%3A%20A%20Parable%20for%20People%2C%20Power%2C%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Justice%20Chandrachud%2C%20taking%20the%20cover%20of%20the%20principle%20of%20complete%20justice%20and%20turning%20justice%20on%20its%20head%20for%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20has%20also%20ensured%20that%C2%A0%20the%20cauldron%20remains%20boiling%20forever.%20His%20order%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20has%20now%20opened%20a%20floodgate%20for%20more%20such%20claims.%20The%20BJP%20or%20the%20RSS%20could%20not%20have%20imagined%20that%20its%20cause%20would%C2%A0%20be%20made%20to%20look%20so%20just%20by%20the%20judiciary%20and%20it%20would%20not%20need%20to%20take%20recourse%20to%20violence%20to%20achieve%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20will%20also%20get%20credit%20for%20decisively%20shaking%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20nation.%20It%20was%20widely%20expected%20that%20his%20bench%20would%20hold%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20constitutional%2C%20but%20he%20went%20a%20mile%20further.%20His%20bench%20also%20decided%20that%20if%20the%20federal%20government%20wants%2C%20it%20can%20break%20any%20state%20and%20carve%20out%20a%20part%20of%20it%20as%20a%20Union%20Territory.%20This%20single%20decision%20has%20made%20the%20states%20slaves%20to%20the%20will%20of%20the%20Centre.%20And%20India%2C%20a%20Union%20of%20States%2C%20no%20longer%20exists!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20is%20a%20skilled%20orator%20and%20all%20his%20statements%20suit%20the%20mood%20of%20contemporary%20politics.%20He%20is%20always%20politically%20correct%20in%20his%20out%20of%20court%20orations.%20He%20sounds%20pleasant.%20But%20he%20has%20not%20been%20appointed%20the%20chief%20orator%20of%20this%20country.%20His%20job%20is%20to%20do%20justice.%20Which%20normally%20should%20inconvenience%20the%20strong.%20But%20we%20have%20seen%20him%20and%20his%20colleagues%20asking%20all%20of%20us%20to%20trust%20the%20words%20of%20the%20solicitor%20general.%20The%20same%20SG%20who%20had%20said%20that%20there%20were%20no%20people%20on%20the%20roads%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20that%20the%20court%20had%20closed%20the%20case.%20People%20were%20dropping%20dead%20on%20the%20roads.%20But%20the%20court%20did%20not%20have%20eyes%20and%20the%20state%20had%20its%20ears.%20He%20wants%20people%20to%20trust%20the%20decision%20makers.%20But%20the%20conduct%20of%20decision%20makers%20does%20not%20inspire%20confidence.%20He%20cannot%20use%20this%20admonition%20to%20answer%20a%20just%20question%20as%20to%20why%20the%20bail%20petitions%20of%20all%20the%20critics%20of%20this%20government%20are%20being%20sent%20to%20a%20special%20judge.%20The%20answer%20cannot%20be%20that%20he%20had%20to%20be%20trusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1739166839794782291%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ecan%20sing%20Christmas%20carols%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20will%20get%20him%20applause.%20Not%20long%20ago%2C%20in%20one%20of%20his%20lectures%2C%20he%20had%20said%20that%20in%20times%20of%20majoritarianism%2C%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20highest%20court%20increases.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20we%20did%20not%20know%20that%20this%20meant%20that%20the%20court%20would%20interpret%20the%20Constitution%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20majoritarianism%20would%20start%20appearing%20constitutional.%20Does%20it%20not%20lead%20to%20peace%20after%20all%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20is%20an%20academic%20and%20an%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704520796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06112912%2FUntitled-design-6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchandrachud-orator-courtroom-judgments-babri-ayodhya%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Chandrachud%20is%20a%20skilled%20orator.%20He%20is%20always%20politically%20correct%20in%20his%20out%20of%20court%20orations.%20But%20he%20has%20not%20been%20appointed%20the%20chief%20orator%20of%20this%20country.%20His%20job%20is%20to%20do%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchandrachud-orator-courtroom-judgments-babri-ayodhya%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20records%20single-day%20rise%20of%20774%20Covid-19%20cases%2C%20active%20cases%20at%204%2C187%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704518363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fmisc%2F2023-03%2F26%2Ffull%2F20221228145L.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-records-single-day-rise-of-774-covid-19-cases-active-cases-at-4-187-124010600163_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20recorded%20a%20single-day%20rise%20of%20774%20COVID-19%20cases%20while%20the%20number%20of%20active%20cases%20stands%20at%204%2C187%2C%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%20said%20on%20Saturday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-records-single-day-rise-of-774-covid-19-cases-active-cases-at-4-187-124010600163_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.c