%20election%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20two%20lopsided%20votes%20%C2%A0in%202014%20and%202018.%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20administration%20levied%20human%20rights%20sanctions%20against%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20elite%20paramilitary%20force%20Rapid%20Action%20Battalion%20and%20several%20of%20its%20former%20officials%20following%20accusations%20of%20severe%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20enforced%20disappearances%20and%20extrajudicial%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20relationships%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20a%20zero-sum%20vacuum%2C%20where%20every%20nation%20is%20looking%20to%20exert%20their%20own%20individual%20will%20on%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20are%20perceived%20to%20be%20allies%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20hard%20work%20done%20on%20growing%20the%20relationship%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Washington%20has%20seen%20a%20closer%20diplomatic%20relationship%20culminate%20in%20the%20Quad%2C%20along%20with%20Australia%20and%20Japan%2C%20aimed%20almost%20entirely%20at%20deterring%20China%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20US%20sits%20apart%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20argues%20it%20is%20in%20its%20national%20interest%20that%20Hasina%E2%80%99s%20government%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20however%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20somewhat%20thin%20under%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20keynote%20speech%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20foreign%20minister%2C%20M.J.%20Akbar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailystar.net%2Fnews%2Fbangladesh%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnews%2Fsuperpowers-want-puppets-pretend-serve-bangladesh-3496971%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20superpowers%20want%20puppets%20who%20can%20serve%20their%20interest%20because%20Bangladesh%20is%20important%20geopolitically.%20Akbar%20termed%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cliberator%20of%20democracy%20from%20dictatorship%E2%8