ive%20efforts%20of%20Jay%20Verma%20and%20Gyanendra%20Shukla.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20two%20residents%20scripted%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20creative%20journey%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20of%20Tulsi%20from%20being%20just%20another%20run-of-the-mill%20village%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98Youtuber%20Village%E2%80%99%20began%20with%20the%20ideation%20and%20creative%20efforts%20of%20Jay%20Verma%20and%20Gyanendra%20Shukla%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246877%2Fsaving-tiger-india-reserve-chhattisgarh-jharkhand-wildlife-trust-of-india-udanti-sitanadi-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20locals%3C%2Fa%3E%20here.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20is%20a%2031-year-old%20teacher-turned-YouTuber.%20Though%20he%20prefers%20not%20to%20listen%20to%20praises%20about%20himself%2C%20he%20is%20known%20to%20be%20popular%20among%20his%20students%2C%20and%20has%20a%20passion%20for%20visual%20art.%20He%20dreams%20of%20making%20films%20one%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGyanendra%2C%20who%20is%20Jay%E2%80%99s%20friend%2C%20was%20working%20as%20a%20network%20engineer%20in%20a%20good%20company%20until%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20YouTube%20was%20a%20relatively%20new%20platform%20for%20rural%20areas%20like%20theirs.%20They%20decided%20to%20explore%20it%20as%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20require%20a%20significant%20investment.%20While%20Jay%20realised%20the%20importance%20of%20originality%20and%20started%20handling%20creative%20aspects%2C%20Gyanendra%20focused%20on%20the%20technical%20side%20of%20the%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20technical%20knowledge%20comes%20naturally%20to%20me%2C%20so%20as%20a%20side%20hustle%20and%20out%20of%20passion%2C%20we%20began%20making%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gyanendra.%20They%20made%20videos%20with%20the%20children%20from%20their%20village%20and%20eventually%20forme