ful%20for%20anyone%20like%20me%20who%20is%20passionate%20about%20learning%20and%20creating%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hemesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shows%20us%20that%20with%20the%20right%20use%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20one%20can%20use%20the%20vast%20information%20available%20there%20at%20our%20disposal%20to%20change%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703860220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FIMG_4975-min-1703854722-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20monitors%20for%20elderly%20with%20dementia%3F%20Hemesh%20Chadalavada%20from%20Hyderabad%20has%20created%20Alpha%20Monitor%2C%20a%20wearable%20device%20that%20helps%20caregivers%20monitor%20patients%20with%20dementia%20and%20Alzheimer's.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337126%2Fmonitors-for-elderly-hemesh-chadalavada-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Two%20Techies%20Are%20Helping%20Foresters%20Combat%20Wildlife%20Crimes%20With%20Technology%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20growing%20modernisation%20and%20increasing%20population%2C%20the%20line%20between%20civilisation%20and%20the%20wild%20has%20become%20increasingly%20blurry.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20humans%20have%20been%20known%20to%20encroach%20upon%20areas%20designated%20for%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20human-animal%20conflict%20has%20raised%20issues%20worldwide.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20rarest%20animals%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20encompassing%20over%2024%20percent%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F130976%2Findia-forest-tree-green-cover%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20forest%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20wildlife%20crime%20is%20alarmingly%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20look%20back%20at%20our%20ancestors%2C%20we%20realise%20that%20perpetrating%20atrocities%20upon%20innocent%20wildlife%20has%20been%20a%20sport%20for%20humans.%20Whether%20hunting%20them%20for%20pleasure%20or%20exploiting%20their%20skin%2C%20teeth%2C%20and%20bones%20for%20our%20benefit%2C%20we%20have%20exploited%20them%20for%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Government%20implementing%20rules%20and%20laws%20to%20protect%20the%20wild%2C%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime%20remain%20staggeringly%20high.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2F112-tigers-deaths-from-january-to-july-this-year-says-wildlife-trust-of-india-1241859.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%202020%20alone%2C%20there%20were%20more%20than%201%2C000%20registered%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Ftamil-nadu-highest-number-wildlife-crimes-southern-states-rti-query-8846758%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20that%20in%202023%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20reported%20150%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime%2C%20while%20Karnataka%20reported%2070%20instances%20of%20wildlife%20crimes%20and%2017%20incidents%20of%20poaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20judicial%20system%20in%20place%20for%20such%20crimes%2C%20the%20question%20of%20why%20wildlife%20crimes%20are%20on%20the%20rise%20persists.%20Faced%20with%20similar%20concerns%2C%20two%20tech%20enthusiasts%2C%20Allen%20Shaji%20and%20Sobin%20Mathew%20from%20Kerala%20combined%20their%20technological%20expertise%20and%20passion%20for%20the%20wild%20to%20digitally%20document%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161753%2Fias-hero-uttar-pradesh-tribes-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20wildlife%20crimes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20This%20not%20only%20eliminates%20bureaucracy%20and%20paperwork%20but%20also%20expedites%20the%20delivery%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFighting%20wildlife%20crime%20with%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Allen%20and%20Sobin%20were%20college%20buddies%20who%20completed%20their%20graduation%20from%20Amalguri%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLike%20any%20other%20engineering%20graduates%2C%20we%20were%20also%20looking%20for%20job%20opportunities.%20I%20got%20placed%20at%20a%20company%20and%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20offer%20letter%20to%20arrive%20in%202016%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20might%20not%20want%20to%20do%20a%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Allen%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sobin%20Mathew%20and%20Allen%20Shaji%2C%20co-founders%20of%20Leopard%20Tech%20Labs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen