0for%20opportunities%20in%20the%20sector%20and%20tried%20reaching%20various%20conservationists.%20We%20met%20with%20Mr%20Jose%20Louie%2C%20who%20also%20was%20from%20our%20hometown.%20He%20was%20from%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20Of%20India%20who%20helped%20us%20secure%20our%20first%20project%20with%20them.%20The%20project%2C%20named%20Mapper%2C%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20our%20collaboration.%20Upon%20successfully%20completing%20this%20project%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20our%20ideas%20have%20more%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20they%20incorporated%20the%20company%20%E2%80%98Leopard%20Tech%20Labs%E2%80%99.%20Currently%2C%20they%20have%20launched%20several%20products%20that%20help%20combat%20wildlife%20crime%20and%20have%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20eight%20countries.%20They%20inform%20that%20they%20are%20also%20in%20collaboration%20with%20different%20State%20Governments%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98HAWK%E2%80%99%20for%20speedy%20justice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20incorporating%20their%20company%2C%20Allen%20and%20Sobin%20began%20working%20as%20consultant%20software%20developers%20for%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20period%20that%20they%20seized%20an%20opportunity%20to%20collaborate%20with%20the%20Kerala%20Forest%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20and%20with%20their%20support%2C%20our%20company%20was%20able%20to%20make%20HAWK%20or%20Hostile%20Activity%20Watch%20Kernel%20with%20the%20forest%20department%20of%20Kerala%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1-1703859196.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22representative%20image%20only%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%